丹·艾克洛德在家人影响下深信且迷恋超自然现象，本片源自他的设想<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="VanityFair2014">{{cite web | first = Lesley M. M. | last = Blume | website = [[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]] | access-date = 2021-11-09 | url = https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/ghostbusters-making-of | title = The Making of Ghostbusters: How Dan Aykroyd, Harold Ramis, and "The Murricane" Built "The Perfect Comedy" | date = 2014-06-04 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210923143000/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/ghostbusters-making-of | archive-date = 2021-09-23 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。他爸写过《鬼魂史》<ref name="THR2016">{{cite web | first = Stephen | last = Galloway | title = The Making of a Comedy Classic: Director Ivan Reitman Spills the Secrets Behind the Original Ghostbusters | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/ghostbusters-director-ivan-reitman-making-911408/ | date = 2016-07-15 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-11-09 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211101002711/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/ghostbusters-director-ivan-reitman-making-911408/ | archive-date = 2021-11-01 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，妈妈自称见过鬼，祖父尝试用无线电和死者交流，曾祖父以信奉招魂术出名。1981年艾克洛德在《[[美国心灵学研究会|美国心灵学研究会期刊]]》看到[[量子力学|量子力学]]文章，由此想到捉鬼。他对现代化演绎20世纪中期喜剧鬼片很感兴趣，如[[艾博特与科斯蒂洛|艾博特与科斯蒂洛]]系列（《[[两傻怪屋捉妖记|两傻怪屋捉妖记]]》，1941年）、[[鲍勃·霍普|鲍勃·霍普]]主演的《[[古堡捉妖记|古堡捉妖记]]》（1940年）、[[鲍沃里男儿|鲍沃里男儿]]系列（《[[追鬼人|追鬼人]]》，1951年）。<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="Esquire">{{cite web | first = Jason | last = Matloff | title = An Oral History of Ghostbusters | url = https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/news/a27498/ghostbusters-oral-history/ | website = [[时尚先生_(刊物)|Esquire]] | date = 2014-02-24 | access-date = 2021-11-09 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210906153034/https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/news/a27498/ghostbusters-oral-history/ | archive-date = 2021-09-06 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

艾克洛德编剧时打算与好友且同样出身《[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]》的[[約翰·貝魯西|約翰·貝魯西]]和[[艾迪·墨菲|艾迪·墨菲]]共同主演，没想到贝鲁西1982年3月死于意外<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="VanityFair2014" />。艾克洛德记得制片人兼星探[[伯尼·布里尔斯坦|伯尼·布里尔斯坦]]来电告知时，他还在写贝鲁西的台词<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。同样曾在《周六夜现场》与艾克洛德合作的比尔·默瑞接受邀请，而且没像惯常那样订立明确协议<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。艾克洛德向布里尔斯坦提出三男捉鬼构想并附“棉花糖人”草图，把人物比作害虫防治工作者：“联系捉鬼敢死队就像找人抓老鼠（一样平常）”<ref name="Esquire" />。伊万·雷特曼此前的《[[動物屋|動物屋]]》（1978年）和《[[杂牌军东征|杂牌军东征]]》（1981年）表现不俗，艾克洛德觉得可以请他导演<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。贝鲁西在世时雷特曼就知道电影大致情节，故事发生在未来，还有许多跨星系捉鬼人士，“拍成电影大概需要两亿美元”<ref name="Esquire" />{{refn|group="注"|1983年落实丹·艾克洛德原版构想所需两亿美元相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Inflation|US|200000000|1983}}美元。}}。艾克洛德的[[剧本前制论述|剧本前制论述]]长70到80页，内容基调更严肃、更吓人<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="Esquire" />。

雷特曼在洛杉矶[[斯蒂迪奥城|斯蒂迪奥城]]亚特熟食店与艾克洛德会谈，告知对方的构想不可能拍成电影，建议剧情集中在地球，这样其中的超自然内容会更幽默。如果一开始就注重立足现实，最后的棉花糖人也会更可信。雷特曼还希望在捉鬼敢死队开业前详述来历，毕竟“20世纪80年代开始大家都在做生意”。<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="Esquire" />两人会后前往[[伯班克_(加利福尼亚州)|伯班克]][[华纳兄弟制片厂|华纳兄弟制片厂]]与雷米斯碰头，雷特曼根据此前多次合作经验认为，与艾克洛德相比，雷米斯更能把剧本朝想要的方向变更<ref name="Esquire" />。雷特曼还觉得雷米斯应该扮演捉鬼敢死队员，后者看过剧本后马上加入项目<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。

剧本需要大幅改写，但雷特曼1983年3月就向[[哥倫比亞影業|哥倫比亞影業]]高管[[弗兰克·普赖斯|弗兰克·普赖斯]]推荐《捉鬼敢死队》。普赖斯认为剧本构想很有趣，但喜剧片往往利润有限，而且特效和人气演员阵营需要高昂预算。<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="Esquire" />雷特曼表示2500至3000万美元就能拍完{{refn|group="注"|1984年的2500至3000万美元相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|25000000|1983}}}}至{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|30000000|1983}}}}美元。}}，普赖斯于是要求电影最迟在同年六月上映<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="THR2016" />。文献对雷特曼当时宣称的数目记载不一，他事后自承纯属编造，只是按《杂牌军东征》预算的三倍计算，当时觉得“合理”<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。此时剧本还没写完，特效公司、开拍日期均未确定，所有工作必须在13个月内完成<ref name="THR2016" />。雷特曼聘请合作过的乔伊·麦迪贾克与迈克尔·格罗斯担任[[电影制片人|副制片人]]<ref name="McCabe-2016">{{cite magazine| last = McCabe | first = Joseph | year = 2016 | title = Bustin' Out a Classic | magazine = The Complete SFX Guide to Ghostbusters | location = United Kingdom | url = https://archive.org/details/SFX.Special.Edition.The.Complete.Guide.to.Ghostbusters.2016.True.PDF/page/n13/mode/2up | access-date = 2021-11-16}}</ref>{{rp|18}}哥伦比亚影业首席执行官[[费伊·文森特|费伊·文森特]]派律师迪克·盖洛普到洛杉矶要求普赖斯不要投资本片，后者不同意。盖洛普回到总部汇报时称普赖斯已经“失控”<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="Esquire" />。

[[环球影业|环球影业]]旗下拥有20世纪70年代儿童节目《[[捉鬼降妖队|捉鬼降妖队]]》版权，英语名称“{{lang|en|The Ghost Busters}}”与《捉鬼敢死队》（“{{lang|en|Ghostbusters}}”）基本相同，为免侵权争议，电影曾考虑《阻鬼敢死队》、《打鬼敢死队》、《灭鬼敢死队》等片名<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="Collider2013">{{cite web | first = David | last = Kobylanski | title = You Know Who To Call Part 1: A Detailed History of the ''Ghostbusters'' Movies, Cartoons, Comics, and Merchandise | url = https://collider.com/ghostbusters-history-movies-cartoons-comics/ | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210921061045/https://collider.com/ghostbusters-history-movies-cartoons-comics/ | date = 2013-10-31 | archive-date = 2021-09-21 | website = [[Collider|Collider]] | access-date = 2021-11-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="TelegraphJun16">{{cite web | first = Rebecca | last = Hawkes | title = Ghostbusters: 10 things you didn't know about the original movie | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308133358/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2016/06/08/slimer-was-played-by-a-peanut-and-other-surprising-ghostbusters/ | website = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2016-06-08 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2016/06/08/slimer-was-played-by-a-peanut-and-other-surprising-ghostbusters/}}</ref>。电影策划期间普赖斯与哥伦比亚影业分道扬镳，当上[[环球影业|环球影业]]总裁，此时他已将《捉鬼敢死队》按50万美元加一个百分点电影利润的价格卖给哥伦比亚影业。根据好莱坞制片商用于人为抬高电影制作成本、限制版税或税务支出的[[好莱坞会计学|好莱坞会计学]]实践，本片从技术上来说没有为环球影业带来分毫利润。<ref name="Esquire" /><ref name="Collider2013" /><ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.theatlantic.com/business/archive/2011/09/how-hollywood-accounting-can-make-a-450-million-movie-unprofitable/245134/ | title = How Hollywood Accounting Can Make a $450 Million Movie 'Unprofitable' | last = Thompson | first = Derek | date = 2011-09-14 | website = [[大西洋_(雜誌)|The Atlantic]] | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211008032059/https://www.theatlantic.com/business/archive/2011/09/how-hollywood-accounting-can-make-a-450-million-movie-unprofitable/245134/ | archive-date = 2021-10-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 编剧 ===
艾克洛德、雷米斯、雷特曼开始改写剧本，起初是在雷特曼的办公室，后前往[[麻薩諸塞州|麻薩諸塞州]][[马萨葡萄园岛|马萨葡萄园岛]]以便专心创作，避免同家人接触。艾克洛德在岛上有房子，三人在地下室夜以继日地工作两周。<ref name="THR2016" />艾克洛德自认倾向[[範圍蔓延|描绘现代生活不光彩的方面]]，重写剧本时主要负责营造风趣情境，创作超自然术语，雷米斯负责精炼笑料和对白。三人各行其事再相互修改，名人鬼魂出没的精神病院、[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]加油站非法关押鬼魂的设施等大量情节被删。<ref name="VanityFair2014" />1983年6月中旬，三人写完初稿并离开马萨葡萄园岛，八月上旬完工的第三稿已同最终定稿相差无几<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="RollingJuly2016">{{cite magazine | first = Jennifer | last = Wood | title = Ivan Reitman: Why We're Still Talking About Ghostbusters 30 Years Later | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/ivan-reitman-why-were-still-talking-about-ghostbusters-30-years-later-226806/ | magazine = Rolling Stone | date = 2016-07-06 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210517175909/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/ivan-reitman-why-were-still-talking-about-ghostbusters-30-years-later-226806/}}</ref>。默瑞拍完《[[刀锋走险|刀锋走险]]》后飞抵纽约与艾克洛德和雷米斯会晤，对剧本和即将扮演的人物没提什么意见。雷米斯曾多次为默瑞演出的电影编剧，自认很清楚应该怎么做。<ref name="VanityFair2014" />

三人创作早期就同意雷米斯扮演的队员负责出谋划策，艾克洛德的角色拍板，默瑞对外发声<ref name="Esquire" />。艾克洛德从虚构人物[[原型|原型]]汲取灵感，自称“彼得·威克曼、雷·史坦茲、伊根·史賓格勒三人相加就等于[[稻草人_(綠野仙蹤)|稻草人]]、[[膽小獅|膽小獅]]、[[錫樵夫|錫樵夫]]”<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。他本想捉鬼敢死队需听从老板指示，雷米斯觉得没必要，三人最好保持自主。雷米斯的构想令人物更加鲜明：彼得是冷静的现代推销员；雷讲究诚信，对技术充满热忱；伊根是实事求是、为人坚忍的知识分子。<ref name="McCabe-2016" />{{rp|18}}

雷特曼认为编剧时最大的挑战就是确立剧情目标，如大反派的身份和目的、鬼魂为何现身、巨大的棉花糖人又如何出现。艾克洛德原有设想包含许多像棉花糖人般复杂的超自然实体，计划在电影开场20分钟就从[[東河_(紐約市)|东河]]涌现。雷特曼觉得构思很好，但对这样的情节以真实角度呈现颇感担心。雷特曼此时还在寻找合适的特效公司，最后在马萨葡萄园岛工作的两周内选定[[理查德·艾德兰德|理查德·艾德兰德]]。<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="DOGMay2016">{{cite web | first = Craig | last = Thomas | title = Ghostbusters: saluting the effects of the original movie | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/movies/ghostbusters-saluting-the-effects-of-the-original-movie/ | website = Den of Geek | date = 2016-05-18 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210517175909/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/ivan-reitman-why-were-still-talking-about-ghostbusters-30-years-later-226806/ | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 选角与人物 ===
[[File:2009_CUN_Award_Party_William_Atherton_008.JPG|thumb]]（摄于2009年）扮演[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]检查员沃尔特·派克]]

制片商认为默瑞是《捉鬼敢死队》大卖的关键，但他一向要很迟才承诺加入项目。普赖斯同意为默瑞寄予厚望的《刀锋走险》注资，觉得就算走眼也亏不了多少钱，希望此举推动默瑞加入《捉鬼敢死队》。<ref name="VanityFair2014" />[[米高·基頓|米高·基頓]]、[[切維·切斯|切維·切斯]]、[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]、[[羅賓·威廉斯|羅賓·威廉斯]]、[[斯蒂夫·古根伯格|斯蒂夫·古根伯格]]、[[李察·普瑞爾|李察·普瑞爾]]都曾表达意向<ref name="AFI" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Adrienne| last = Tyler | title = Ghostbusters Cast: The Actors Who Almost Played The Main Characters | url = https://screenrant.com/ghostbusters-movie-characters-actors-almost-cast-venkman-spengler/ | website =  Screen Rant | date = 2020-03-15 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210805232044/https://screenrant.com/ghostbusters-movie-characters-actors-almost-cast-venkman-spengler/ | archive-date = 2021-08-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="TelegraphCast">{{cite web | first = Robbie | last = Collin | title = Who Are You Calling A Washed-Up Superhero? | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/film/birdman/michael-keaton-interview/ | website = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2015-02-25 | access-date = 2020-11-22 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20201122065607/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/film/birdman/michael-keaton-interview/ | archive-date = 2020-11-22 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，剧组曾考虑邀请基顿、[[克里斯托弗·沃肯|克里斯托弗·沃肯]]、[[约翰·利思戈|约翰·利思戈]]、[[克里斯托弗·劳埃德|克里斯托弗·劳埃德]]、[[傑夫·高布倫|傑夫·高布倫]]扮演伊根<ref name="TelegraphCast" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Holly | last = Pyne | url = https://www.shortlist.com/news/30-ghostbusters-facts | title = 30 things you (probably) didn't know about Ghostbusters | website =  ShortList | date = 2011-08-17 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211011011157/https://www.shortlist.com/news/30-ghostbusters-facts | archive-date = 2021-10-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。雷米斯从杂志封面抽象建筑获得灵感设计伊根的外表，身穿三件套粗花呢西装，头戴金属框边眼镜且头发竖直。人物姓氏源自德国史学家[[奧斯瓦爾德·斯賓格勒|奧斯瓦爾德·斯賓格勒]]，名字取自雷米斯的匈牙利难民同学。<ref name="Esquire" />除三大男主角外，剧中人物基本由麦迪贾克负责选角<ref name="McCabe-2016" />{{rp|19}}。厄尼·哈德森为出演溫斯頓·雷德莫爾先后试镜五次<ref name="VanityFair2014" />，自称早期剧本的温斯顿戏份更多，是背景复杂的空军爆破专家。哈德森对此非常高兴，在片酬只有往常一半的情况下同意接演，却在开拍前晚拿到戏份大幅删减的新剧本，对此雷特曼告知哈德森，是制片商要求扩充默瑞的戏码。<ref name="EWNov2014">{{cite web | first = Ernie | last = Hudson | url = https://ew.com/article/2014/11/05/ghostbusters-ernie-hudson/ | title = The painful what-if that haunts 'Ghostbuster' Ernie Hudson | website = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2014-11-05 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210720035114/https://ew.com/article/2014/11/05/ghostbusters-ernie-hudson/ | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-date = 2021-07-20 | dead-url = no}}</ref>艾克洛德称原计划请墨菲饰演温斯顿，但雷特曼表示没这事儿<ref name="PeopleJun2014" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Bradford | last = Evans | title = The Lost Roles of Eddie Murphy | url = https://www.vulture.com/2011/04/the-lost-roles-of-eddie-murphy.html | website =  Vulture | date = 2011-04-07 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210613154513/https://www.vulture.com/2011/04/the-lost-roles-of-eddie-murphy.html | archive-date = 2021-06-13 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[格雷戈里·海因斯|格雷戈里·海因斯]]、维尔约翰逊都曾是温斯顿扮演人选<ref>{{cite web | first = Brian | last = Cronin | title = Movie Legends Revealed: How ''Ghostbusters'' Marginalized Winston | url = https://www.cbr.com/movie-legends-revealed-how-ghostbusters-marginalized-winston/ | website = Comic Book Resources | date = 2016-07-14 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210821022306/https://www.cbr.com/movie-legends-revealed-how-ghostbusters-marginalized-winston/ | archive-date = 2021-08-21 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Ryan | last = Parker | title = 'Family Matters' Actor Reginald VelJohnson Says Everyone Still Thinks He's A Cop | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/reginald-veljohnson-talks-comedy-action-840152/ | date = 2015-11-16 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210629035029/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/reginald-veljohnson-talks-comedy-action-840152/ | archive-date = 2021-06-29 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

[[戴露·漢娜|戴露·漢娜]]、[[丹尼斯·克罗斯比|丹尼斯·克罗斯比]]、[[茱莉娅·罗伯茨|茱莉娅·罗伯茨]]参与达娜·巴雷特试镜，最后西格妮·韦弗入选。韦弗此前在《[[異形_(電影)|异形]]》（1979年）、《[[危險年代|危險年代]]》（1982年）扮演的都是严肃人物，剧组起初不看好她。韦弗自称在[[耶鲁大学大卫·格芬戏剧学院|耶鲁戏剧学院]]就颇具喜剧表演天赋，试镜时手脚并用“行走”并像狗一样嚎叫。<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="Esquire" /><ref>{{cite web  | first = Fred | last = Topel | title = 'Ghostbusters' Documentary Has New Surprises About the Classic Comedy and You Can Watch It for Free | date = 2020-06-18 | website = CheatSheet.com | archive-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.cheatsheet.com/entertainment/ghostbusters-documentary-has-new-surprises-about-the-classic-comedy-and-you-can-watch-it-for-free.html/ | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210817022451/https://www.cheatsheet.com/entertainment/ghostbusters-documentary-has-new-surprises-about-the-classic-comedy-and-you-can-watch-it-for-free.html/}}</ref>祖鲁附身达娜源自她的建议，雷特曼表示此举令人物同事态形成利害关系，解决最后一幕面临的问题<ref name="THR2016" />。韦弗还建议把人物职业从模特儿换成音乐家，称达娜或许有些恪守教条，但看到她拉大提琴，观众自然会相信她有头脑、有灵魂<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。

[[约翰·坎迪|约翰·坎迪]]谢绝出演路易斯·塔利的邀请，向雷特曼表示不太理解人物，建议另请带德国口音的演员并配上几条[[德國牧羊犬|德國牧羊犬]]，但主创觉得这会导致片中的狗太多。雷特曼把剧本寄给合作过的莫拉尼斯，后者一小时后同意出演。<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="Esquire" /><ref name="RollingJuly2016" />莫拉尼斯提出许多建议，如塔利的会计职业、聚会时冗长的即兴演讲<ref name="RollingJuly2016" />。安妮·波茨在[[桑德拉·伯恩哈德|桑德拉·伯恩哈德]]谢绝后获得出演捉鬼敢死队秘书珍妮·梅尔尼兹的机会，戏份开拍当天抵达片场。雷特曼要求她赶快上镜演出，波茨马上换掉便服并借用布景师的眼镜，故而梅尔尼兹自始至终都戴着眼镜。<ref name="HuffPoSep2014">{{cite web | title = Ghostbusters Turns 30! Here's How Bill Murray, Dan Aykroyd, Harold Ramis Ended Up Making Timeless Comedy | url = https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/09/03/ghostbusters-bill-murray-harold-ramis-dan-aykroyd_n_5758398.html | website = [[赫芬顿邮报|HuffPost]] | date = 2014-09-03 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308202743/https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/09/03/ghostbusters-bill-murray-harold-ramis-dan-aykroyd_n_5758398.html | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Esquire" />

威廉·阿瑟顿参演[[百老匯|百老匯]]剧目《[[百老汇_(舞台剧)|百老汇]]》后获选饰演沃尔特·派克。派克与[[玛格丽特·杜蒙|玛格丽特·杜蒙]]在[[馬克思兄弟|馬克思兄弟]]电影中的作用类似，都是喜剧陪衬。阿瑟顿表示，派克必须对捉鬼敢死队的魅力视而不见，心存愤恨，这一点儿都不好笑。<ref>{{cite web | first = Kyle | last = Ryan | title = William Atherton | url = https://www.avclub.com/william-atherton-1798219915 | website = [[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]] | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210714061508/https://www.avclub.com/william-atherton-1798219915 | archive-date = 2021-07-14 | dead-url = no | date = 2010-04-21 | access-date = 2021-11-10}}</ref>[[苏美尔|苏美尔]]神祇戈泽原定请[[保罗·雷宾斯|保罗·雷宾斯]]出演，人物形象是身穿商务西装的建筑师。雷宾斯谢绝邀请，剧组改请南斯拉夫女演员斯拉维扎·乔万，人物形象调整为融合[[格雷斯·琼斯|格雷斯·琼斯]]与[[大卫·鲍伊|大卫·鲍伊]]外貌特征的[[雙性性格|双性人]]。<ref name="HuffPoSep2014" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Claire | last = Stokoe | title = 10 of Our Favorite Sexy Badass Female Horror Characters | website = Dread Central | date = 2016-02-11 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.dreadcentral.com/news/150323/10-of-our-favorite-sexy-badass-female-horror-characters/ | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211107012021/https://www.dreadcentral.com/news/150323/10-of-our-favorite-sexy-badass-female-horror-characters/ | archive-date = 2021-11-07 | access-date = 2021-11-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Bradford | last = Evans | title = The Lost Roles of Ghostbusters | archive-date = 2021-05-19 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.vulture.com/2011/05/the-lost-roles-of-ghostbusters.html | website = [[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]] | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210519163837/https://www.vulture.com/2011/05/the-lost-roles-of-ghostbusters.html | date = 2011-05-05 | access-date = 2021-11-10}}</ref>乔万的斯拉夫口音很重，故戈泽由帕迪·爱德华兹配音，但演员表没列他的名字<ref name="AFI" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Drew | last = Mackie | title = Celebrate 25 Years of The Little Mermaid with 25 Things Even Superfans May Not Know | url = https://people.com/celebrity/the-little-mermaid-25th-anniversary/ | website =  People | date = 2014-09-03 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210801142320/https://people.com/celebrity/the-little-mermaid-25th-anniversary/ | archive-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 摄制 ===
[[File:55_Central_Park_West_(Ghostbusters_Building)_by_David_Shankbone.jpg|thumb]]

电影1983年10月28日在纽约启动[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="BTMSep14">{{cite web | first = Kevin | last = Stern | title = Beyond the Marquee: The Web-Series (Episode 70) – The ''Ghostbusters'' Ecto-1 Car and Designer Stephen Dane | url = http://beyondthemarquee.com/34980 | website = Beyond the Marquee | date = 2014-09-18 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210517180317/http://beyondthemarquee.com/34980 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。雷特曼当天就把默瑞带到片场，此时还不肯定他是否看过剧本<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。纽约的摄制工作经过六周在圣诞节前收尾<ref name="THR2016" />，雷特曼希望避免演职人员面对纽约12月的恶劣天气，力图尽快拍完<ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016">{{cite web | first = Jared | last = Cowan | title = Ivan Reitman Looks Back at the Original Ghostbusters' L.A. Locations | website = LA Weekly | date = 2016-07-07 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.laweekly.com/ivan-reitman-looks-back-at-the-original-ghostbusters-l-a-locations/ | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308144635/https://www.laweekly.com/ivan-reitman-looks-back-at-the-original-ghostbusters-l-a-locations/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08}}</ref>。此时在纽约拍电影颇具风险，20世纪80年代初，纽约在许多人眼中等同财政灾难和暴力，洛杉矶才是娱乐业中心。雷特曼2014年接受采访时称，当年选择纽约是因为“我希望该片是……我的纽约电影”。<ref name="VanityFair2014" />雷特曼鼓励几位擅长喜剧的主演临场发挥，每场戏都多拍几遍，保留有价值的演员创意，同时引导大家回归剧本<ref name="RollingJuly2016" />。

剧组在城内标志地点拍摄未经事先安排的自发镜头，例如[[洛克斐勒中心|洛克斐勒中心]]追逐演员的都是真保安，根本不知道是在拍电影<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。群众演员高呼“捉鬼敢死队”的镜头是在[[第八大道|中央公园西]]取景，但片名此时尚未确定。麦迪贾克敦促哥伦比亚影业争取许可，以“捉鬼敢死队”为片名。<ref name="Esquire" />

[[中央公园西55号|中央公园西55号]]大楼是片中达娜的家，也是片尾捉鬼敢死队与戈泽高潮大战所在地。美术部加装地板，利用[[接景|接景]]、模型、数字效果装饰营造鬼魂活动焦点。<ref name="FSR" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Steven | last = Gaines | url = https://nymag.com/nymetro/realestate/vu/14943/ | title = One Apartment, 75 Years | date = 2005-10-28 | website = [[紐約_(雜誌)|New York]] | archive-date = 2021-09-03 | dead-url = no | archive-url= http://web.archive.org/web/20210903002916/https://nymag.com/nymetro/realestate/vu/14943/}}</ref><ref name="DigitalSpyMay2015">{{cite web | first = Joshua | last = Winning | title = How to tour New York City like a Ghostbuster – from Dana's Central Park apartment to Ghostbusters HQ | url = https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a795108/ghostbusters-tour-new-york-city-your-favourite-locations-from-ghostbusters-hq-to/ | website = [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] | date = 2016-05-24 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308210515/https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a795108/ghostbusters-tour-new-york-city-your-favourite-locations-from-ghostbusters-hq-to/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>片尾戏码摄制期间，纽约市当局同意在[[繁忙時間|繁忙時間]]关闭邻近街道，影响市内大范围交通。据格罗斯回忆，大家站在楼顶还能看到汽车一直排队到[[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]。执法人员与市民的小冲动在各处上演，警察拔枪警告拒绝听从指挥的司机，或是把司机从豪华轿车窗口拖出来。愤怒的市民质问麦迪贾克到底在拍什么鬼玩意儿，后者声称是[[弗朗西斯·科波拉|弗朗西斯·科波拉]]在拍《[[棉花俱樂部|棉花俱樂部]]》（1984年）。艾克洛德偶遇非常崇拜的科幻作家[[艾萨克·阿西莫夫|艾萨克·阿西莫夫]]，后者对电影摄制不无怨言：“你们这些人带给大楼诸多不便，糟透了，真不明白你们怎么脱身的！”<ref name="Esquire" />[[曼哈顿圣三一路德会堂|曼哈顿圣三一路德会堂]]紧挨中央大道西55号，片尾踩在棉花糖人脚下<ref name="DigitalSpyMay2015" />。
[[File:Ghostbusters_Firehouse.jpg|thumb]]

电影在[[纽约市政厅|纽约市政厅]]<ref name="DigitalSpyMay2015" />、[[纽约公共图书馆|纽约公共图书馆]]<ref name="AFI" />、[[林肯表演藝術中心|林肯表演藝術中心]]<ref>{{cite web | first = David | last = Ng | title = Lincoln Center fountain, Star Of 'Ghostbusters' And 'Moonstruck,' Reopens | date = 2009-10-02 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2010-01-23 | url = https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/culturemonster/2009/10/lincoln-center-fountain-star-of-ghostbusters-and-moonstruck-reopens-after-renovations.html | website = Los Angeles Times | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20100123164138/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/culturemonster/2009/10/lincoln-center-fountain-star-of-ghostbusters-and-moonstruck-reopens-after-renovations.html}}</ref>、[[哥倫布圓環|哥倫布圓環]]、[[第五大道|第五大道]][[欧文信托|欧文信托银行]]<ref>{{cite web| last = Budin | first = Jeremiah | title = The Ultimate Ghostbusters Map Guide To New York City | url = https://ny.curbed.com/maps/the-ultimate-ghostbusters-map-guide-to-new-york-city | website = Curbed | date = 2014-10-07 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210707215109/https://ny.curbed.com/maps/the-ultimate-ghostbusters-map-guide-to-new-york-city | archive-date = 2021-07-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[綠苑酒廊|綠苑酒廊]]取景，地处[[翠貝卡|翠貝卡]]的[[梯形消防站公司8号|梯形消防站公司8号]]充当捉鬼敢死队总部<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="PeopleJun2014" /><ref name="Wallace-2015">{{cite book | last = Wallace | first = Daniel | year = 2015 | title = Ghostbusters: The Ultimate Visual History | publisher = Insight Editions | location = [[圣拉菲尔_(加利福尼亚州)|San Rafael, California]] | isbn = 978-1-6088-7510-8}}</ref>{{rp|31–32, 38–39, 48}}。哥伦比亚大学同意电影用该校[[哈维迈耶大厅|哈维迈耶大厅]]充当片中虚构的韦弗堂，但不得显现学府之名<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|31–32, 38–39, 48}}。

演职人员转战洛杉矶，在圣诞节至新年期间继续拍摄<ref name="THR2016" />。片中采用实景特效，需要的熟练技术人员大多住在洛杉矶，所需的[[片場系統|片場系統]]纽约更是完全没有<ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" />。《捉鬼敢死队》的故事发生在纽约，但大部分镜头是在洛杉矶或位于伯班克的制片厂外景地摄制。选址侦探根据在纽约拍摄的楼房在洛杉矶搜寻适当建筑，复制纽约楼盘内景。<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" />雷特曼想拍梯形消防站公司8号内景，但消防站还在使用，没有足够空闲时间供剧组拍摄，最后改在洛杉矶市中心废弃的[[洛杉矶23号消防局|23号消防局]]摄制。梯形消防站公司8号的设计在纽约很常见，但在洛杉矶很罕见。捉鬼敢死队办公室挂有1915年23号消防局人员档案照片。<ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" />

演职人员在纽约公共图书馆主阅览室拍摄时必须早早开始并在上午十点前收尾<ref name="DOGMay2016" />，地下图书馆书库用[[理查德·里奥丹中央图书馆|洛杉矶中央图书馆]]代替，雷特曼声称两者完全可以互换<ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" />。片中虚构的塞吉威克酒店其实是[[比尔特莫尔千禧酒店|比尔特莫尔千禧酒店]]<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|47–48}}。经过55至62天摄制，主体拍摄在1984年1月收尾<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="TestedMay15">{{cite web | first = David | last = Konow | title = Putting Together Ghostbusters' Special Effects | url = https://www.tested.com/art/movies/524482-putting-together-ghostbusters-special-effects/ | website =  Tested.com | date = 2015-05-07 | access-date = 2020-08-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20200810223414/https://www.tested.com/art/movies/524482-putting-together-ghostbusters-special-effects/ | archive-date = 2020-08-10 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

=== 后期制作 ===
电影制作周期短，发行期限临近，促使雷特曼边拍边剪，许多镜头根本没时间多拍几遍<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="DOGMay2016" />。雷特曼有时觉得制作特效充斥的电影实在麻烦，特效镜头需要[[分鏡|分鏡]]并提前拍摄，没法重来或新增镜头。格罗斯对此表示：“先要分镜，效果就像先行剪辑。拍的镜头需要他们批准，我们再花九个月来剪辑。这其中没有保险、没有备用镜头，一次都不能出错。你只能剪，不能增，对雷特曼限制很大，对此他非常厌烦。”<ref name="TestedMay15" />

雷在“德梅林堡”和女鬼发生性接触的桥段被剪，原计划用于为艾克洛德的角色增加情侣。雷米斯觉得剧情发展很快，显得这场戏多余，雷特曼于是把桥段改成电影中场梦境。<ref>{{cite web | first = Ethan | last = Anderton | title = A 'Ghostbusters' Deleted Scene from 1984 Has Been Unearthed | url = https://www.slashfilm.com/549346/ghostbusters-1984-deleted-scene/ | website =  /Film | date = 2017-02-17 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210926231921/https://www.slashfilm.com/549346/ghostbusters-1984-deleted-scene/ | archive-date = 2021-09-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>剪辑师谢尔顿·卡恩在电影摄制期间就把黑白电影胶片发给导演，雷特曼认为这不但便于修改，而且有助于把握影片节奏。电影摄制完工三周后，卡恩就完成第一轮全面剪辑，<ref name="THR2016" />电影终剪版本长105分钟<ref name="AFI" />。

=== 音乐 ===
{{Listen|filename=Ghostbusters 1984 Elmer Bernstein Score Sample.ogg|pos=right| title = 埃尔默·伯恩斯坦：主题|format=[[Ogg|Ogg]]|description=伯恩斯坦为捉鬼敢死队谱写的“滑稽”主题，在电影的喜剧和严肃基调间争取平衡<ref name="Larson-1985">{{cite magazine | last = Larson | first = Randall D. | year = 1985 | title = Elmer Bernstein and Ghostbusters | magazine = CinemaScore: The Film Music Journal | issue = 13/14 | location = United States | url = https://cnmsarchive.wordpress.com/2013/09/06/elmer-bernstein-and-ghostbusters/comment-page-1/ | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210224150721/https://cnmsarchive.wordpress.com/2013/09/06/elmer-bernstein-and-ghostbusters/comment-page-1/ | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-10 | pages = 9—10}}</ref>}}
[[埃尔默·伯恩斯坦|埃尔默·伯恩斯坦]]谱写本片[[電影配樂|配乐]]，拥有72名乐手的[[好莱坞交响乐团|好莱坞交响乐团]]在[[西洛杉矶|西洛杉矶]][[村庄录音室|村庄录音室]]演奏，乐曲由大卫·斯皮尔与伯恩斯坦之子[[彼得·伯恩斯坦|彼得]]编排<ref name="Larson-1985" /><ref name="TheVillage">{{cite web | title = Recorded at The Village – Elmer Bernstein's 'Ghostbusters' Score | dead-url = yes | url = http://villagestudios.com/recorded-at-the-village-elmer-bernsteins-ghostbusters-score/ | website = The Village | access-date = 2019-06-22 | archive-date = 2019-06-22 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20190622191851/http://villagestudios.com/recorded-at-the-village-elmer-bernsteins-ghostbusters-score/}}</ref>。埃尔默已多次同雷特曼合作，早在演员签约前就加入项目<ref name="Larson-1985" />。雷特曼希望配乐脚踏实地、立足现实，而不是提醒观众什么地方好笑<ref name="TestedMay15" />。伯恩斯坦用[[馬特諾音波琴|馬特諾音波琴]]（相当于键盘乐器[[特雷門|特雷門]]）营造“诡异”音效，但擅长这种乐器的人很少，只能到英格兰邀请。他使用的还有三台[[雅马哈DX7|雅马哈DX7]]合成器。<ref name="Larson-1985" /><ref name="TheVillage" />伯恩斯坦1985年接受采访时称，《捉鬼敢死队》是他作曲最难的电影，在平衡各种喜剧和严肃基调上极具挑战。他自认为捉鬼敢死队谱写的“滑稽”主题“可爱又不致过火”，还觉得电影后半部配乐相当容易，只要听起来“神秘且令人敬畏”。<ref name="Larson-1985" />

导演和伯恩斯坦在创作早期就打算片中部分桥段播放流行音乐，补充作曲家谱写的原创曲段。如鬼魂逃出捉鬼敢死队总部时响起米克·斯迈利的歌曲《魔法》，捉鬼敢死队音乐主题后由[[小雷·帕克尔|小雷·帕克尔]]的[[捉鬼敢死队_(歌曲)|电影同名歌曲]]代替。<ref name="Larson-1985" /><ref name="TheVillage" />伯恩斯坦本人对片中采用这些歌曲、特别是《魔法》不以为然，但对歌曲登上畅销金曲榜前十的成绩颇感难以辩驳<ref name="Larson-1985" />。

电影中场蒙太奇需要背景音乐，[[休易·路易斯与新闻|休易·路易斯与新闻]]乐队的《[[想要新药|想要新药]]》因节奏合拍临时占位，雷特曼后经他人介绍与帕克尔面谈，后者谱写类似曲段匹配蒙太奇<ref name="Esquire" />。帕克尔介入前已有艺人为本片创作50至60首主题歌，但导演觉得都不合适<ref name="CBCJul16">{{cite web | first = Melody | last = Lau | url = https://www.cbcmusic.ca/posts/12032/15-things-you-might-not-know-about-the-ghostbuster | title = 15 Things You Might Not Know about the Ghostbusters Theme Song | date = 2016-07-14 | website = CBC Music | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210906164410/https://www.cbcmusic.ca/posts/12032/15-things-you-might-not-know-about-the-ghostbuster | archive-date = 2021-09-06 | access-date = 2021-09-06 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="MediumJul16">{{cite web | first = Mike | last = Pizzo | title = The Freaky Legacy of the Ghostbusters Theme Song | url = https://medium.com/cuepoint/the-ghastly-legacy-of-the-ghostbusters-theme-song-28094f0e71a1 | website = [[Medium|Medium]] | date = 2016-07-14 | access-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-date = 2021-08-10 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210810145418/https://medium.com/cuepoint/the-ghastly-legacy-of-the-ghostbusters-theme-song-28094f0e71a1}}</ref>。剧组联系[[休易·路易斯|休易·路易斯]]谱写电影主题曲，但他已同意加入《[[回到未来|回到未来]]》（1985年）<ref name="AFI" />。

== 设计 ==
业界主要特效公司在本片制作的13个月间均忙于其他项目，其他公司又不足以应付《捉鬼敢死队》需要的630个特效镜头。特效摄影理查德·艾德兰德此时打算从[[光影魔幻工業|光影魔幻工業]]离职自立门户，雷特曼推动哥伦比亚影业与同样需要特效公司的[[米高梅|米高梅]]联手，向艾德兰德预支五百万美元创办[[老板影业|老板影业]]。<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="THR2016" />据艾德兰德回忆，律师用大部分前期准备时间敲定合同，最后用来创办特效公司、拍摄镜头、合成画面的时间一共只有十个月<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。老板影业团队分组完成《捉鬼敢死队》和米高梅公司科幻片《[[威震太陽神|威震太陽神]]》所需特效<ref name="AFI" />。500万美元特效超预算70万<ref name="DOGMay2016" />，摄制时间太紧，所以大部分特效镜头必须一步到位<ref name="TestedMay15" />。格罗斯督导老板影业成立，还需监督大批概念设计师的聘请过程，如漫画图书画师[[塔尼诺·利伯拉托尔|塔尼诺·利伯拉托尔]]（作品未采纳）、[[伯尼·莱特森|伯尼·莱特森]]（协助设计鬼魂）、[[分鏡|分镜画师]]汤姆·恩里克斯的设计促成“洋葱头鬼”<ref name="McCabe-2016" />{{rp|19}}。

=== 怪物特效 ===
艾德兰德曾参与1982年鬼片《[[鬼哭神號|鬼哭神號]]》，为鬼怪设计积累经验。格罗斯认为，一方面要让人觉得鬼确实有威胁，另一方面又要切合电影倾向喜剧的基调，其中平衡很不简单。<ref name="McCabe-2016" />{{rp|22}}<ref>{{cite magazine | last = McCabe | first = Joseph | year = 2016 | title = Ghostly Visions | magazine = The Complete SFX Guide to Ghostbusters | location = United Kingdom | access-date = 2021-11-11 | url = https://archive.org/details/SFX.Special.Edition.The.Complete.Guide.to.Ghostbusters.2016.True.PDF/page/n25/mode/2up}}</ref>布偶会发出难闻的气味，特效美编[[史蒂夫·约翰逊_(特效美编)|史蒂夫·约翰逊]]于是在片场雕出粘乎乎的绿色贪吃鬼，当时叫“洋葱头鬼”<ref name="TelegraphJun16" /><ref name="BDJun2018">{{cite web | first = John | last = Squires | title = FX Master Steve Johnson on Creating Slimer With the Help of Cocaine and John Belushi's Ghost [Exclusive] | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no | url = https://bloody-disgusting.com/exclusives/3495677/special-fx-master-steve-johnson-creating-slimer-cocaine-fueled-frenzy-exclusive/ | website = Bloody Disgusting | date = 2018-04-26 | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210225131421/https://bloody-disgusting.com/exclusives/3495677/special-fx-master-steve-johnson-creating-slimer-cocaine-fueled-frenzy-exclusive/}}</ref>，后在1986年电视动画《[[捉鬼特工队|捉鬼特工队]]》获名“斯林姆”<ref name="AFI" />。设计斯林姆耗时半年，耗资约30万美元。制片商高管插手要求尽快完成设计，绞尽脑汁的约翰逊至少吸食三克[[可卡因|可卡因]]用一整夜完工，形象一定程度上遵照艾克洛德与雷米斯的要求向贝鲁西致敬。<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="Esquire" /><ref name="BDJun2018" /><ref name="Waddell-2016">{{cite magazine | last = Waddell | first = Callum | year = 2016 | title = Slimer Designer | magazine = The Complete SFX Guide to Ghostbusters | location = United Kingdom | url = https://archive.org/details/SFX.Special.Edition.The.Complete.Guide.to.Ghostbusters.2016.True.PDF/page/n39/mode/2up | access-date = 2021-11-11 | page = 42}}</ref>马克·威尔逊身穿全尺寸[[泡沫橡胶|泡沫橡胶]]布偶站在黑色背景前拍摄，布偶师用线缆操纵模型动作<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="Waddell-2016" /><ref name="McCabe-2016C">{{cite magazine | last = McCabe | first = Joseph | year = 2016 | title = Making Magic | magazine = The Complete SFX Guide to Ghostbusters | location = United Kingdom | access-date = 2021-11-10 | url = https://archive.org/details/SFX.Special.Edition.The.Complete.Guide.to.Ghostbusters.2016.True.PDF/page/n77/mode/2up}}</ref>{{rp|80,82}}。

艾克洛德请朋友“维京人”设计棉花糖人，要求融[[必比登|米其林人]]与头戴水手帽的[[面团宝宝|面团宝宝]]形象于一身<ref name="Esquire" />。特效艺师兼演员比尔·布莱恩制作棉花糖人外形并化妆，步行动作模仿[[哥斯拉|哥斯拉]]。扮演棉花糖人的泡沫套装共有18套，每套成本2.5至3万美元，其中替身演员汤米·塞萨尔身穿的17套在拍摄期间焚毁。<ref name="DOGMay2016" /><ref name="McCabe-2016C" />{{rp|82}}泡沫有毒，故布莱恩使用独立供氧。套装上有三个头，用泡沫和玻璃纤维制成，带有不同表情而且能在线缆控制下完成不同动作。拍摄时套装旁有比例模型，以突显棉花糖人的庞大。特效组只找到一种警车模型比例合适，买下多辆并修改来代表各种汽车。水无法按比例缩小，遥控汽车撞击导致消防栓爆裂喷出的水其实是沙子。<ref name="DOGMay2016" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Story Notes for Ghostbusters | url = https://www.amc.com/talk/2014/07/story-notes-for-ghostbusters | website = [[AMC_(电视频道)|AMC.com]] | date = 2014 | access-date = 2019-06-23 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20190623204312/https://www.amc.com/talk/2014/07/story-notes-for-ghostbusters | archive-date = 2019-06-23 | dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Bill Bryan – The Wizard of Foam and Plastic | url = https://www.stanwinstonschool.com/artists/bill-bryan-fabricator-innovator-performer | website = [[斯坦·温斯顿|stanwinstonschool.com]] | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171003162411/https://www.stanwinstonschool.com/artists/bill-bryan-fabricator-innovator-performer | archive-date = 2017-10-03 | dead-url = no}}</ref>捉鬼敢死队炸毁棉花糖人后如雪花般飘向人群的“棉花糖”其实是递须膏。计划用于喷射的递须膏重68公斤，阿瑟顿看到后坚持先测试，结果重量太大，特技演员摔倒在地，实际拍摄时只用一半。递须膏刺激皮肤，拍摄数小时后部分演员起皮疹。<ref name="Esquire" />

僵尸出租车司机布偶同样由约翰逊雕刻，根据他为《[[美国狼人在伦敦|美国狼人在伦敦]]》（1981年）制作的复活尸体布偶设计，只有该布偶戏码是在纽约摄制<ref name="McCabe-2016C" />{{rp|80}}。他和威尔逊一起制作图书馆幽灵布偶，用20条穿过躯干的线缆操控，头部和双臂可移动，还能扯掉躯干的橡胶皮肤，从人形变成可怕的食尸鬼<ref name="McCabe-2016C" />{{rp|81}}。剧组担心原版图书馆幽灵吓到小观众，后在电影《[[天师斗僵尸|天师斗僵尸]]》（1985年）使用<ref name="IndieWireJun2012" />。[[卡片目錄|图书馆目录]]桥段采用实景拍摄，共拍三次，工作人员用铜管把卡片吹得乱飞。每次拍摄必须收拢并摆好卡片，雷特曼采用多台摄像机同步拍摄，一边聚焦图书馆员，一边用广角镜头拍摄人物周围乱飞的卡片。<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="DOGMay2016" />飞在空中的图书是用细线吊起<ref name="DOGMay2016" />。

[[兰德尔·威廉·库克|兰迪·库克]]负责为戈泽手下恶犬祖鲁和文茨制作一比四的可移动比例模型[[定格动画|定格动画]]布偶。模型非常笨重，为制作狗穿过街道追逐路易斯的镜头，单在片场摄制模型移动九米就耗费近30小时。<ref name="McCabe-2016C" />{{rp|81}}达娜在光线笼罩的门前被恶魔之手按在椅子上，雷特曼自承这场戏受《[[第三類接觸_(電影)|第三类接触]]》（1977年）影响。剧组使用橡胶门拍摄，方便将门挤压变形，营造神秘力量企图穿门而过的效果。操作员藏身椅子后面的活板门，用恶魔犬腿形状手套穿破椅子。<ref name="DOGMay2016" />此时[[電腦成像|電腦成像]]技术尚未面世，所有不用布偶营造的鬼魂只能靠动画制作，一秒钟画面需时三周<ref name="DOGMay2016" />。乔万为扮演戈泽戴着红色隐形眼镜导致眼部巨痛，在片场走动时她还戴着保护带<ref name="FSR" />。

=== 技术和设备 ===
捉鬼敢死队大部分代表装备由硬件顾问斯蒂芬·戴恩负责设计，如用于对付鬼的“质子背包”，捉鬼陷阱、捉鬼车。电影计划1983年9月开拍，上述设备必须提前六周完成设计和制作。<ref name="BTMSep14" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Andrew | last = Liszewski | url = https://gizmodo.com/meet-the-man-who-designed-ghostbusters-most-iconic-prop-1636848858 | title = Meet the Man Who Designed Ghostbusters' Most Iconic Props in Two Weeks | date = 2014-09-19 | website = [[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]]| access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210228232251/https://gizmodo.com/meet-the-man-who-designed-ghostbusters-most-iconic-prop-1636848858 | archive-date = 2021-02-28 | dead-url = no}}</ref>质子背包灵感源自军用[[火焰喷射器|火焰喷射器]]，上有可形成“中微子棒”的手持式质子流发生器，通过软管连接据称装有核加速器的背包<ref name="Collider2013" /><ref name="WiredJul17">{{cite magazine | first = Rene | last = Chun | title = Inside The Deeply Nerdy—And Insanely Expensive—World Of Hollywood Prop Collecting | url = https://www.wired.com/2017/03/super-expensive-hollywood-props/ | magazine = [[连线|Wired]] | date = 2017-03-07 | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210516051108/https://www.wired.com/2017/03/super-expensive-hollywood-props/ | archive-date = 2021-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。戴恩自称“回家用烂泡沫和别的东西堆在一起，看起来像那么回事儿。东西要高度机械化，看起来必须是现成的，像是多余的军事装备。”<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|55–56}}

雷特曼微调设计后，最终在银幕亮相的质子背包模型外壳是玻璃纤维，用螺栓把铝背板固定在[[多用途轻型个人携带设备|美国陆军背包框架]]上<ref name="WiredJul17" />。每个背包加上照明用电池约重14公斤，拍长镜头时导致演员背部拉伤<ref name="DOGMay2016" /><ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|55–56}}。剧组备有两个轻型背包，其一为中空但外表一致，用于拍摄远景画面，另一个是泡沫橡胶制成，用于动作场面<ref name="DOGMay2016" /><ref name="WiredJul17" />。特效总监查克·加斯帕尔根据戴恩的设计制作玻璃纤维道具，用橡胶模制作完全相同的玻璃纤维外壳<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|55–56}}。“中微子棒”顶端的[[闪光灯|闪光灯]]为动画师绘制质子流提供原点<ref name="DOGMay2016" />。剧组用假墙配合烟火技术，营造质子流造成破坏的效果<ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" />。“精神动力能量计”道具是用艾奥纳SP-1手持式擦鞋机做底，上面固定照明和电子设备<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|59}}。技术装备设计避免花哨和光亮，突出人物科学背景和自制设备的特点<ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" />。

艾克洛德的初版剧本写有捉鬼车，他和约翰·达维基斯为车辆设计提供早期构想。戴恩绘制捉鬼车内外详细图纸，督导工作人员把1959年产[[凯迪拉克米勒－流星|凯迪拉克米勒－流星]]改装成捉鬼车。<ref name="DriveJul16">{{cite web | first = Sean | last = Evans | title = 11 Facts About the ''Ghostbusters'' Ecto-1 You Never Knew | url = https://www.thedrive.com/vintage/4415/11-facts-about-the-ghostbusters-ecto-1-you-never-knew | website = Drive | date = 2016-07-14 | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210204043838/https://www.thedrive.com/vintage/4415/11-facts-about-the-ghostbusters-ecto-1-you-never-knew | archive-date = 2021-02-04 | dead-url = no}}</ref>据艾克洛德透露，片中捉鬼车是“救护车改装成灵车，又改回救护车”<ref name="THREctomobile">{{cite web | first = Graeme | last = McMillan | title = 'Ghostbusters' Fans Get Chance to Build Their Own Ectomobiles | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/ghostbusters-fans-get-chance-build-own-ectomobile-1216405/ | date = 2019-06-07 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308144722/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/ghostbusters-fans-get-chance-build-own-ectomobile-1216405}}</ref>。早期构想是用黑色汽车配上紫色和白色闪光灯，产生超自然意味光芒，但在摄影师[[拉兹洛·科瓦奇|拉兹洛·科瓦奇]]指出晚上拍深色漆效果不理想后作罢。捉鬼车的构想还有奇幻色彩，如分解物质和跨维度旅行功能。剧组购买两辆车，另一辆用于改装前的镜头。<ref name="DriveJul16" />戴恩设计的高科技屋顶设施包括定向天线、空调机组、储物箱、[[雷达天线罩|雷达天线罩]]<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|41–42}}。受尺寸限制，屋顶支架空运到曼哈顿，捉鬼车则是用火车拉到[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]<ref name="BTMSep14" />。音效设计[[理查德·贝格斯|理查德·贝格斯]]录制豹子咆哮的声音，经过剪辑并倒着播放充当报警音效<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|41–42}}。

=== 商标与布景 ===
[[File:ProhibitionSign2.svg|thumb]]

根据艾克洛德创作的剧本，捉鬼敢死队制服和捉鬼车上的商标主体是[[不得标志|不得标志]]和困住的鬼魂，是“维京人”的原创构想<ref name="CreativeReview" /><ref name="NationalPostJun1414">{{cite web | first = Chris | last = Knight | title = Cultural Studies: Why ''Ghostbusters'' matters, and 10 things you probably didn't know about the movie | date = 2014-06-14 | website = [[国家邮报|National Post]] | archive-date = 2019-08-09 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://archive.today/20190809211407/https://nationalpost.com/entertainment/movies/cultural-studies-why-ghostbusters-matters-and-10-things-you-probably-didnt-know-about-the-movie | access-date = 2021-11-11 | url = https://nationalpost.com/entertainment/movies/cultural-studies-why-ghostbusters-matters-and-10-things-you-probably-didnt-know-about-the-movie}}</ref>。最终设计由自愿充当本片[[藝術總監|美术总监]]的格罗斯负责。道具与布景都需要商标，故需尽快确定图案，格罗斯与老板影业画师兼生物设计顾问布伦特·博茨合作，博茨画出定稿，[[R/GA|R/GA]]为片头制作商标动画。格罗斯称商标有两版，其一在斜线位置有“捉鬼敢死队”字样。他对商标外观不满意，将其翻转，斜线变成左上至右下，随后众人决定去掉文字。格罗斯称，电影在欧洲发行显示的商标才是“正确”版本，美国的不得标志斜线是左下至右上，美国公映版显示的商标也是如此。<ref name="CreativeReview" />

麦迪贾克聘请约翰·德奎尔任[[美術指導|美術指導]]<ref name="RollingJuly2016" />。剧本没有明确戈泽从何处现身，德奎尔根据剧本在达娜所住公寓楼顶画出打开的巨大水晶门<ref name="RollingJuly2016" />。剧组在伯班克制片厂地段12号录音棚建造片中虚构的中央公园西55号屋顶，布景规模在电影史上名列前茅，周围是360度巨幅环形绘画。绘画期间的照明消耗大量电力，制片厂只能在需要使用时加装四台发电机并切断别处供电。<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Bryan | last = Alexander | title = Ghostbusters: Five scary facts about the 1984 classic | url = https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/08/29/ghostbusters-comedy-classic-cigarette/14829681/ | date = 2014-08-31 | website = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20201212190743/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2014/08/29/ghostbusters-comedy-classic-cigarette/14829681/ | archive-date = 2020-12-12 | dead-url = no}}</ref>为制作背景动画，剧组还用细线吊起飞机等小模型<ref name="THR2016" />。布景搭在离地三层楼高，以便从下方角度摄制<ref name="DOGMay2016" />。

布景重建达娜所住公寓楼的最下面三层和邻街部分用于拍摄，如片尾高潮部分的地震桥段，剧组用液压设备抬升破碎的街道<ref name="FSR" /><ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|38–39}}。支离破碎的道路与实际位置隔开，用于两组镜头无缝衔接<ref name="LAWeeklyJul2016" />。德奎尔称：“大家要在一个晚上时间内装扮街道。下午众人回家时一切正常，早上老太太溜狗时整条街就像火山爆发。人们自然纷纷向纽约警局投诉，总机响个不停。”<ref name="Wallace-2015" />{{rp|39}}公寓楼向外爆炸的特技镜头开拍时韦弗就在现场<ref name="DOGMay2016" />，她在空中旋转的镜头是在片场用替身结合机械臂达成，雷德曼根据与魔术师[[道格·亨宁|道格·亨宁]]合作学来的经验把机械臂藏在窗帘里<ref name="FSR" />。

== 发行 ==
=== 试映与营销 ===
《捉鬼敢死队》于1984年2月3日[[试映|试映]]，此时特效镜头尚未完工，以便判断电影喜剧效果。雷特曼觉得棉花糖人与电影其余部分的现实风格背道而驰，担心观众不买账。<ref name="RollingJuly2016" />他还记得约有两百人在街头接受邀请走进伯班克地段影院观看试映，到图书馆开馆桥段时他就知道稳了。图书馆员变成怪物时观众有些害怕，又有人大笑，还有人报以掌声。<ref name="RollingJuly2016" />决定命运的棉花糖人桥段反响类似，雷特曼深知无需再重拍任何镜头<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="RollingJuly2016" />。面向业界同行的试映反响不及普通观众，普赖斯记得自己大笑时，其他观众只是面无表情地坐着，他认为这只是同行不希望本片成功。默瑞与艾克洛德的经纪人[[迈克尔·奥维茨|迈克尔·奥维茨]]记得某高管言道：“别担心，我们别会犯错误”；但哥伦比亚影业母公司[[可口可乐公司|可口可乐]]董事长[[罗伯特·戈伊苏埃塔|罗伯特·戈伊苏埃塔]]一度表示：“老天，咱们的衣服都要输没啦。”<ref name="VanityFair2014" /><ref name="EWJun2000">{{cite web | first = Joshua | last = Rich | title = High Spirits | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2000-06-09 | url = https://ew.com/article/2000/06/09/ghostbusters-technology-remembered/ | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210224173525/https://ew.com/article/2000/06/09/ghostbusters-technology-remembered/ | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

电影首映前数月发布的悬念式预告片以“鬼怪免进”商标为主，确保图案早早深入人心，在不透露片名和明星身份的前提下推动观众兴趣<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="EWanniverinterview">{{cite web| first = Jeff | last =  Labrecque | title =1984: 'Ghostbusters' | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2014-11-07 | url = https://ew.com/article/2014/11/07/1984-ghostbusters/ | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210225072651/https://ew.com/article/2014/11/07/1984-ghostbusters/ | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。另有院线预告片包含[[受話方付費電話|受話方付費電話]]号码，打通后可与默瑞和艾克洛德通话，前后六周里每小时约有千人致电<ref name="TelegraphJun16" />，两人还在院线业主大会“ShoWest”为本片宣传<ref>{{cite web | first = Anthony | last = Breznican | title = Watch Bill Murray and Dan Aykroyd hustle theater owners in 'Ghostbusters' clip | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2019-04-05 | url = https://ew.com/movies/2019/04/05/bill-murray-dan-aykroyd-found-ghostbusters-clip/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210714164618/https://ew.com/movies/2019/04/05/bill-murray-dan-aykroyd-found-ghostbusters-clip/ | archive-date = 2021-07-14 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。哥伦比亚影业花费约一千万美元营销经费，其中印刷品225万，宣传品100万，700万广告和杂项开支包括首映式媒体食宿和医院开销<ref name="NYTimesJan87">{{cite web  | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1987/01/28/movies/where-movie-ticket-income-goes.html?pagewanted=all | title = Where Movie Ticket Income Goes | website= The New York Times | date = 1987-01-28 | access-date = 2021-11-11 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308230906/https://www.nytimes.com/1987/01/28/movies/where-movie-ticket-income-goes.html?pagewanted=all | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。考虑预算和营销费用，估计本片至少要进账八千万美元才能获利<ref name="McCabe-2016" />{{rp|22}}。

=== 票房 ===
{{see also|1984年电影}}
《捉鬼敢死队》1984年6月7日在[[韋斯特伍德_(加利福尼亞州)|韦斯特伍德]]阿夫柯影院[[首演|首映]]，次日再在北美洲1339家院线公映<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="BOMMain">{{cite web | title = Ghostbusters | website = Box Office Mojo | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3696592385/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210809004324/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3696592385/ | archive-date = 2021-08-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。电影在美国和加拿大公映首周末收入1360万美元，平均每家电影院10040美元{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|13600000|1984}}}}{{Inflation/year|US}}美元。}}，领先同样新上映的恐怖喜剧片《[[小精靈_(電影)|小精灵]]》（1250万美元），以及上映第三周的冒险片《[[魔宮傳奇|魔宮傳奇]]》（1200万美元）登顶票房榜<ref name="BOMMain" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1984 Weekend 23: June 8-10, 1984 | website = Box Office Mojo | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1984W23/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210628055424/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1984W23/ | archive-date = 2021-06-28 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。影片公映首周票房增至2310万美元{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|23100000|1984}}}}美元。}}，是《[[杜絲先生|杜絲先生]]》（1982年）后哥伦比亚影业首部票房大片<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="EWJun2000" /><ref name="BOMWeekly">{{cite web | title = Ghostbusters (1984) – Weekly Box Office Results | website = Box Office Mojo | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3696592385/weekly/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211111163804/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3696592385/weekly/ | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Kate | last = Meyers | title = A Bill Murray filmography | date = 1993-03-19 | website = Entertainment Weekly | url = https://ew.com/article/1993/03/19/bill-murray-filmography/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308133008/https://ew.com/article/1993/03/19/bill-murray-filmography/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《捉鬼敢死队》连续七周登顶票房榜，收入近1.47亿美元，直到八月上旬才被《[[紫雨_(电影)|紫雨]]》挤下<ref>{{cite web | title = 'Purple Rain' Ousts 'Ghostbusters' as No. 1 | website = The New York Times | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 1984-08-01 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/08/01/movies/purple-rain-ousts-ghostbusters-as-no-1.html | page = C22 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210517180428/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/08/01/movies/purple-rain-ousts-ghostbusters-as-no-1.html | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | access-date = 2021-11-12 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = 'Ghostbusters' Grosses Near 'Indiana Jones' | website = The New York Times |  agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] |date = 2021-11-12 | access-date = 2021-11-12 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/07/12/arts/ghostbusters-grosses-near-indiana-jones.html | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210307204952/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/07/12/arts/ghostbusters-grosses-near-indiana-jones.html | archive-date = 2021-03-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1984 Week 30: July 27-August 2, 1984 | website = Box Office Mojo | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1984W30/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308152207/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1984W30/}}</ref>。一周后本片回归榜首，随后连续五周排第二，仅次于动作片《[[赤色黎明_(1984年电影)|赤色黎明]]》或惊悚片《[[黑色手铐|黑色手铐]]》<ref>{{cite web | title = 'Ghostbusters' Regains Top Spot at Box Office | website = The New York Times | agency = United Press International | date = 1984-08-08 | dead-url = no | page = C15 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210307214821/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/08/08/arts/ghostbusters-regains-top-spot-at-box-office.html | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/08/08/arts/ghostbusters-regains-top-spot-at-box-office.html | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-date = 2021-03-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1984 Week 32: August 10-16, 1984 | website = Box Office Mojo | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308174358/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1984W32/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1984W32/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Domestic 1984 Week 33: August 17–23, 1984 | website = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2021-11-12 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1984W33/ | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308120446/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekly/1984W33/}}</ref>。《捉鬼敢死队》连续16周位居票房榜三甲，十月下旬才逐渐跌出前十，公映30周后才在1985年初下线<ref name="BOMWeekly" /><ref name="EWApr14">{{cite web | first = Jeff | last = Labrecque | title = 'Ghostbusters': Best Summer Blockbuster No. 8 | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2014-04-18 | url = https://ew.com/article/2014/04/18/ghostbusters-best-summer-blockbuster/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210811121218/https://ew.com/article/2014/04/18/ghostbusters-best-summer-blockbuster/ | archive-date = 2021-08-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。电影很快就成为卖座大片，超越《魔域奇兵》登顶暑期票房榜，2.29亿美元进账在[[1984年电影|1984年电影]]排第二{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|229000000|1984}}}}美元。}}，比12月中旬上映的艾迪·墨菲主演动作喜剧《[[比佛利山警探|比佛利山警探]]》只少五百万美元<ref name="RollingJuly2016" /><ref name="HTRJun16">{{cite web | first = Pamela | last = McClintock  | title = Box Office: How 'Ghostbusters' Compares to the First Two Films | url= https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/box-office-how-ghostbusters-compares-911792/ | date = 2016-07-19 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20201108194632/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-how-ghostbusters-compares-911792 | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。此外，《捉鬼敢死队》还打破《动物屋》的喜剧片历史票房纪录，直到半年后被《比佛利山警探》超越<ref name="THR2016" /><ref name="EWApr14" /><ref name="HTRJun16" />。

根据谈判条款，哥伦比亚影业可拿走半数或扣除花销后的九成票房，从中选择偏高的一种。从实际表现来看第二种明显更高，制片商拿到七成三票房利润，估计达1.28亿美元。<ref name="NYTimesJan87" />{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|128000000|1984}}}}美元。}}主要演员拿到毛利或净利分成<ref name="AFI" />，《洛杉矶时报》1987年发文估计单默瑞就进账两到三千万美元<ref>{{cite web | first = Leonard  | last = Klady | title = Ghostly Movies| url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-05-17-ca-380-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1987-05-07 | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210517180008/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-05-17-ca-380-story.html | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|20000000|1984}}}}至{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|30000000|1984}}}}美元。}}。美加以外国家和地区的票房缺乏详细纪录，估计为5300万美元，把影片全球总票房提升到2.82亿美元<ref name="BOMMain" />{{refn|group="注"|相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|282000000|1984}}}}美元。}}同年许多电影日后成为80年代的标志，如《小精灵》、《[[小子難纏|小子難纏]]》、《[[终结者|终结者]]》、《[[猛鬼街|猛鬼街]]》、《[[綠寶石_(電影)|绿宝石]]》、《[[大魔域|大魔域]]》。此外，1984年还是电影史上首次出现四部作品票房过亿。<ref>{{cite web | first = Tim | last = Robey | title = Why 1984 was the best year ever for popcorn cinema | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/10955829/Why-1984-was-the-best-year-ever-for-popcorn-cinema.html | website = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2014-07-10 | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308180246/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/10955829/Why-1984-was-the-best-year-ever-for-popcorn-cinema.html | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

1985年8月《捉鬼敢死队》在美国和加拿大重新发行，前后五周收入940万美元，票房总额升至2.39亿美元<ref>{{cite web | title = Ghostbusters (1985 Re-release) | website = Box Office Mojo | dead-url = no | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3663037953/weekly/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308133525/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3663037953/weekly/ | access-date = 2021-11-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Ghostbusters (1984) | website = Box Office Mojo| url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt0087332/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211023034514/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt0087332/ | archive-date = 2021-10-23 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，从《比佛利山警探》手中夺得80年代喜剧票房冠军宝座<ref name="HTRJun16" />。2014年8月《捉鬼敢死队》30周年之际，电影修复重制版在美加两国七百家院线上映，收入350万美元，票房总额升至2.42亿美元<ref>{{cite web | first = Jeff | last = Labrecque | title = 'Ghostbusters' gets the call for theatrical re-release | website = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2014-06-05 | archive-date = 2021-09-24 | dead-url = no | url = https://ew.com/article/2014/06/05/ghostbusters-rerelease/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210924222001/https://ew.com/article/2014/06/05/ghostbusters-rerelease/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Ghostbusters (30th Anniversary Release) | website = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3646260737/weekly/ | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308194550/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3646260737/weekly/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。影片还在特别活动及其他周年庆限量上映<ref>{{cite web | first = Andrea | last = Seikaly | title = 'Ghostbusters' to Celebrate 30th Anniversary With Theatrical Re-Release | date = 2014-06-05 | website = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | access-date = 2021-11-12 | url = https://variety.com/2014/film/news/ghostbusters-30th-anniversary-theater-re-release-1201214268/ | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308194650/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/ghostbusters-30th-anniversary-theater-re-release-1201214268/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Steven | last = Zeitchik | title = With re-release, can 'Ghostbusters' pull a 'Lion King'? | url = https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/09/ghostbusters-new-revival-movie-lion-king-showtimes-theaters-los-angeles.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1985-09-27 | access-date = 2021-11-12 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210304214828/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/09/ghostbusters-new-revival-movie-lion-king-showtimes-theaters-los-angeles.html | archive-date = 2021-03-04 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，加上其他国家和地区，估计《捉鬼敢死队》的全球收入达2.95亿美元<ref name="BOMMain" />。

== 反响 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
[[File:Bill_Murray-8882.jpg|thumb]]（摄于2018年）的[[冷面笑匠|冷面笑匠]]喜剧表演风格是《捉鬼敢死队》主要亮点]]

《捉鬼敢死队》公映后普受好评<ref name="AFI" /><ref>{{cite web | title = "Ghostbusters'" released | url = https://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/ghostbusters-released | website = [[歷史頻道|History.com]] | date = 2019-06-06 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-10-08 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211008203432/https://www.history.com/this-day-in-history/ghostbusters-released}}</ref>，[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]评分三星半（最高四星），称特效导向[[大片|大片]]与“狡猾”对白如此完美融合的佳作难得一见；他认可本片特效为演员表演服务而非本末倒置，还称壮观特效往往与喜剧相克，本片是罕见的例外。埃伯特指出，身为主流电影，《捉鬼敢死队》能有那么多值得引述的台词实在难得可贵。<ref>{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | author-link = 罗杰·埃伯特 | title = Ghostbusters | website = RogerEbert.com | date = 1984-06-08 | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/ghostbusters-1984 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211029185453/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/ghostbusters-1984 | archive-date = 2021-10-29 | dead-url = no}}</ref>约瑟夫·盖尔米斯在《[[新闻日报|新闻日报]]》把影片归入青少年奇幻片，称捉鬼敢死队总部消防站就像配备[[消防滑杆|消防滑杆]]和捉鬼车的[[蝙蝠洞|蝙蝠洞]]<ref name="RevNewsDay">{{cite web | first = Joseph | last = Gelmis | title = 'Ghostbusters': Newsday's 1984 review of original film | website = Newsday | date = 2016-06-08 | url =  https://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/ghostbusters-newsday-s-1984-review-of-original-film-1.11891998 | access-date =  2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-07-04 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210704114150/https://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/ghostbusters-newsday-s-1984-review-of-original-film-1.11891998}}</ref>。

《[[德瑟雷特新闻报|德瑟雷特新闻报]]》的克里斯托弗·希克斯赞扬雷特曼导演功底更上一层楼，剧组没有把本片拍得像前作《[[瘋狂高爾夫|瘋狂高爾夫]]》与《杂牌军东征》那么粗俗，力争令幽默更具创意，追求真正的惊悚。不过他批评结局“用力过猛”、丧失幽默感，只不过片中那么多“未曾一见的鬼魂”对整体观感不无小补。<ref name="Hicks-1984">{{cite news | last = Hicks | first = Christopher | title = 'Ghostbusters' a funny step forward for crazy trio | work= Deseret News | date = 1984-06-08 | page = W5 | location = Salt Lake City, Utah | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2019-08-15 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=336&dat=19840608&id=AatNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5640,3404745 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190815225815/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=336&dat=19840608&id=AatNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=G4MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5640,3404745 | dead-url = no}}</ref>[[珍妮特·马斯林|珍妮特·马斯林]]同样认为末日般的结局有些失控，影片在小场面捉鬼桥段表现最佳<ref name="RevMaslin">{{cite web | last = Maslin | title = Film: 'Ghostbusters,' with Murray and Aykroyd | website = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 1984-06-08 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/06/08/movies/film-ghostbusters-with-murray-and-aykroyd.html | archive-url  = http://web.archive.org/web/20210224222348/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/06/08/movies/film-ghostbusters-with-murray-and-aykroyd.html | access-date = 2021-11-16 | page = C5 | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | dead-url = no | first = Janet}}</ref>。[[戴夫·凯尔|戴夫·凯尔]]认为雷特曼擅长即兴喜剧，但在特效逐渐升级之际丧失对本片的掌控<ref name="RevKehr">{{cite web | first = Dave | last = Kehr | title = Ghostbusters | url = https://chicagoreader.com/film/ghostbusters-2/ | date = 1984 | website = Chicago Reader | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210608145305/https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/ghostbusters/Film?oid=2456705 | archive-date = 2021-06-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

[[亚瑟·奈特|亚瑟·奈特]]认可《捉鬼敢死队》轻松的喜剧风格，称剧情虽然“原始”，但对创作《[[肉丸_(电影)|肉丸]]》与《动物屋》的团队来说，本片“远比预期更精致、更有格调”，他特别称赞谢尔顿·卡恩与[[大卫·布莱威特|大卫·布莱威特]]的剪辑维持影片喜剧和动作节奏<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-08-11 | dead-url = no | url= https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/ghostbusters-thrs-1984-review-748028/ | title = 'Ghostbusters': THR's 1984 Review | website = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2014-11-11 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210811113212/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/ghostbusters-thrs-1984-review-748028/}}</ref>。[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]认为电影的幽默和视觉噱头不上台面，但连串“胡说八道”的喜剧效果实在令人难以抗拒，可比超自然恐怖片《[[大法師|大法師]]》改请喜剧组合艾博特与科斯蒂洛主演<ref name="RevPeople">{{cite web | author = People Staff | title = Picks and Pans Review: Ghostbusters | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210608145252/https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-ghostbusters-vol-21-no-24/ | url = https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-ghostbusters-vol-21-no-24/ | website = [[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | date = 1984-06-18 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-06-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》刊登[[理查德·席克尔|理查德·席克尔]]的文章，称电影故意恶搞其他鬼片，把特效做得特别“俗气”。在他看来，演职人员高屋建瓴是本片赢得赞誉的重要原因。<ref name="RevSchickel">{{cite magazine | first = Richard | last = Schickel | title = Exercise for Exorcists (Page 1) | magazine = [[時代雜誌|Time]] | date = 1984-06-11 | url = http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,926579,00.html | access-date = August 12, 2019 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090114075221/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,926579,00.html | archive-date = 2009-01-14 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="RevSchickelB">{{cite magazine | first = Richard | last = Schickel | title = Exercise for Exorcists (Page 2) | magazine = Time | date = 1984-06-11 | url = http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,926579-2,00.html | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200216091101/http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,926579-2,00.html | archive-date = 2020-02-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>大卫·安森通过《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》称赞本片堪称团体协作典范，大家“都朝放松乃至精神错乱的目标努力”，是暑期胡说八道电影杰作<ref>{{cite news | last = Ansen | first = David | title = Got a Demon in Your Icebox? | work = [[新闻周刊|Newsweek]] | date = 1984-06-11 | location = New York City | page = 80}}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》发文称本片“制作奢华”，但过上些许时日就会为人遗忘<ref name="RevVariety">{{cite web | title = Ghost Busters | date = 1983-12-31 | website = Variety | url = https://variety.com/1983/film/reviews/ghost-busters-1200426081/ | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210608145705/https://variety.com/1983/film/reviews/ghost-busters-1200426081/ | archive-date = 2021-06-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

影评人一致认可默瑞的演出<ref name="Hicks-1984" /><ref name="RevSchickel" /><ref name="RevSchickelB" /><ref name="RevSiskel">{{cite web | first = Gene | last = Siskel | title = Bill Murray busts loose with ghosts | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/chi-ghostbuster-review-gene-siskel-020140224-story.html | date = 1984-06-08 | website = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308165317/https://www.chicagotribune.com/chi-ghostbuster-review-gene-siskel-020140224-story.html | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Kael-1984">{{cite news | last = Kael | first = Pauline | title = The Pop Junkpile | work = [[紐約客|The New Yorker]] | date = 1984-06-25 | location = New York City | page = 99}}</ref>。[[吉恩·西斯克尔|吉恩·西斯克尔]]认为电影的特效很无聊，幸好有默瑞敏感的喜剧天赋弥补<ref name="RevSiskel" />。《综艺》特别称赞默瑞的肢体与即兴喜剧演出令人青眼相看<ref name="RevVariety" />；希克斯看法类似，觉得默瑞在本片的演出远超以往<ref name="Hicks-1984" />。西斯克尔认为扮演彼得堪称一生难求的机遇，默瑞标志般的喜剧风格在本片充分展现<ref name="RevSchickel" /><ref name="RevSchickelB" />。盖尔米斯赞扬默瑞在剧情局势趋于严肃之际仍然毫不理会，维持电影喜剧基调<ref name="RevNewsDay" />。

默瑞、艾克洛德、雷米斯的演出互动赢得普遍认可<ref name="RevPeople" /><ref name="RevSiskel" />。西斯克尔称赞艾克洛德与雷米斯的“优雅”表现，凸显默瑞的精彩演出<ref name="RevSchickel" /><ref name="RevSchickelB" />。崔維斯与盖尔米斯认为三位主角的合作效果出众<ref name="RevNewsDay" /><ref name="RevPeople" />，希克斯称三位主演似乎“想当80年代的马克斯兄弟”<ref name="Hicks-1984" />。凯尔称艾克洛德与雷米斯的发挥空间尚有不足，不过默瑞念台词时的[[冷面笑匠|冷面笑匠]]作风值得称赞<ref name="RevKehr" />。《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》的[[宝琳·凯尔|宝琳·凯尔]]认为三人间的化学效应尚有不足，除默瑞表现突出外，另外两人的实质贡献有限。在她看来，默瑞的台词表现出色，但往往曲高和寡，无人响应。<ref name="Kael-1984" />马斯林指出，对于那些机智、连贯不足的电影而言，默瑞的才华特别有价值，他饰演的人物往往无所事事，导致剧情沦为次要、为特效服务之际，角色面临的问题仍未解决。不过，马斯林认可韦弗的演出，堪称默瑞的“绝对陪衬”。<ref name="RevMaslin" />《综艺》认为电影邀请多位顶级笑匠出演，但相互缺乏协作实属不智<ref name="RevVariety" />。西斯克尔认可人物互动，但对剧情后期新增哈德森的角色不以为然，人物发展也不足，令人感觉他在片中只是吸引票房的摆设<ref name="RevSiskel" />。

=== 荣誉 ===
《捉鬼敢死队》入围[[第57届奥斯卡金像奖|第57届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|最佳原创歌曲]]（小雷·帕克尔创作的电影同名插曲）、[[奧斯卡最佳視覺效果獎|最佳视觉效果]]（约翰·布鲁诺、理查德·艾德兰德、查克·加斯帕尔、马克·瓦尔戈）两项大奖，分别不敌[[史蒂维·旺德|史蒂维·旺德]]为《[[红衣女郎|红衣女郎]]》创作的插曲《[[电话诉衷肠|电话诉衷肠]]》和电影《魔域奇兵》<ref name="Collider2013" /><ref name="AcademyAwards57">{{cite web | title = The 57th Academy Awards in 1985| url = https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1985 | website = [[奥斯卡金像奖|Oscars.org]] | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211029062339/https://oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1985 | archive-date = 2021-11-16 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-16}}</ref>。本片还入围[[第42届金球奖|第42届金球奖]][[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇電影|最佳影片（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Winners and Nominees in 1985 | url = https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/1985 | website = [[金球獎|GoldenGlobes.com]] | date = 1985 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308122402/https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/1985 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影男主角|最佳电影男主角（音乐剧/喜剧类，默瑞）<ref>{{cite web]]，分别不敌《绿宝石》、《[[双喜临门_(1984年电影)|双喜临门]]》（[[达德利·摩尔|达德利·摩尔]]）、《电话诉衷肠》<ref>{{cite web | title = Winners and Nominees in 1985 (Page 3) | url = https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/1985?page=3 | website = GoldenGlobes.com | date = 1985 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20190629104648/https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/1985?page=3 | archive-date = 2019-06-29 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2019-06-29}}</ref>。帕克尔创作的插曲拿下[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳原创歌曲，艾德兰德入围最佳视觉效果但同样不敌《魔域奇兵》<ref>{{cite web | title = Film in 1985 | url = http://awards.bafta.org/award/1985/film | website = [[英国电影和电视艺术学院|British Academy of Film and Television Arts]] | date = 1985 | access-date = 2021-10-31 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211031050456/http://awards.bafta.org/award/1985/film | archive-date = 2021-10-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，本片还在[[第12届土星奖|第12届土星奖]]角逐拿下[[土星獎最佳奇幻電影|最佳奇幻片奖]]<ref>{{cite web | title = 1984 Film Awards for Best Fantasy Film Release: Winner 'Ghostbusters' | url = https://www.saturnawards.org/The-Saturn-Awards-Past-Winners.php?category=2&year=1984#b | website = [[土星獎|SaturnAwards.org]] | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20181220230944/https://www.saturnawards.org/The-Saturn-Awards-Past-Winners.php?category=2&year=1984 | archive-date = 2018-12-20 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 公映后 ==
=== 余波 === 
[[File:RayParkerJrHWOFMar2013.jpg|thumb]]<ref name="AcademyAwards57" />，休易·路易斯宣称帕克尔剽窃他的歌曲《想要新药》并起诉]]

小雷·帕克尔创作的电影同名插曲登顶1984年[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百强单曲榜]]并保持三周，共上榜21周<ref name="CBCJul16" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Ghostbusters | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210309052141/https://www.billboard.com/music/ray-parker-jr/chart-history/hot-100/song/333215 | url = https://www.billboard.com/music/ray-parker-jr/chart-history/hot-100/song/333215 | website = [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard.com]] | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>，估计歌曲令本片票房加码两千万美元<ref>{{cite book | last = Austin | first = Bruce A. | title = Immediate Seating: A Look at Movie Audiences | year = 1989 | chapter = Which Show to See? | isbn = 978-0-5340-9366-2 | publisher = Wadsworth Publishing | location = Sydney | url = https://books.google.com.sg/books?id=cFMbAQAAIAAJ&q=ghostbusters&redir_esc=y | access-date = 2021-11-16 | page = 78}}</ref>。众多名流在雷特曼执导的同名大卖音乐视频客串出镜<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="CBCJul16" /><ref name="MediumJul16" />。电影公映不久，休易·路易斯以涉嫌剽窃他1983年歌曲《想要新药》的罪名起诉帕克尔<ref name="AFI" /><ref name="MediumJul16" />，案件1985年达成庭外和解<ref name="Esquire" /><ref name="MediumJul16" />，帕克尔后反诉路易斯违反该案保密协议<ref name="MediumJul16" />。1984年，[[鬼马小精灵|鬼马小精灵]]版权方[[哈维漫画|哈维漫画]]起诉哥伦比亚影业要求五千万美元赔偿并销毁所有胶片拷贝，宣称捉鬼敢死队商标是根据哈维漫画持有版权的角色“胖鬼”创作。法庭裁定哥伦比亚影业胜诉。<ref>{{cite web | title = Casper's creators aren't so friendly | url= https://www.upi.com/Archives/1984/11/16/Caspers-creators-arent-so-friendly/1331469429200/ | date = 1984-11-16 | website = [[合众国际社|UPI.com]] | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308162831/https://www.upi.com/Archives/1984/11/16/Caspers-creators-arent-so-friendly/1331469429200/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Samantha | last = Beckett | title = On Remand: Lawyers Ain't Afraid Of No Ghosts | date = 2014-06-19 | url = https://abovethelaw.com/2014/06/on-remand-lawyers-aint-afraid-of-no-ghosts/ | website = Above the Law | archive-url = https://archive.today/20190728113329/https://abovethelaw.com/2014/06/on-remand-lawyers-aint-afraid-of-no-ghosts/ | archive-date = 2019-07-28 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-16}}</ref>

默瑞在本片公映后息影四年，自称《捉鬼敢死队》大卖预示他以后都不会再有更大的成就，个人项目《刀锋走险》惨淡收场更令他心灰意冷。1988年圣诞喜剧《[[孤寒财主|孤寒财主]]》是默瑞此后首度扮演主人翁，<ref>{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | title = Bill Murray, "Quick Change" Artist | date = 1990-07-13 | website = RogerEbert.com | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/interviews/bill-murray-quick-change-artist | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210713081638/https://www.rogerebert.com/interviews/bill-murray-quick-change-artist | archive-date = 2021-07-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="RollingStone" />电影宣传标语称他“回归鬼魂界”<ref name="NationalPostJun1414" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Timothy | last = White | title = The Rumpled Anarchy of Bill Murray | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1988/11/20/magazine/the-rumpled-anarchy-of-bill-murray.html | date = 1988-11-20 | website = The New York Times | access-date = 2021-11-16 | page = 638 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211113003233/https://www.nytimes.com/1988/11/20/magazine/the-rumpled-anarchy-of-bill-murray.html | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。雷特曼1989年接受采访时表示，世人对《捉鬼敢死队》与他的其他作品缺乏尊重，根本没有严肃对待的意愿，令他颇感失望。在他看来，许多人眼中的本片“不过又一部动作喜剧”。<ref name="RollingStone">{{cite magazine | title = 'Ghostbusters II': Return of the Money-Making Slime | date = 1989-06-01 | magazine = [[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210517180011/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/ghostbusters-ii-return-of-the-money-making-slime-235631/ | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/ghostbusters-ii-return-of-the-money-making-slime-235631/}}</ref>

哈德森对《捉鬼敢死队》的感觉很复杂，对原版剧本更加丰满的人物在成片边缘化颇感遗憾，认为电影对他的演艺事业缺乏助力，至少没达到个人期望或他人承诺。哈德森2014年接受采访时自称很喜欢温斯顿，角色不乏优秀台词，感谢影迷认可，但他总觉得人物可有可无，令人爱恨交加，难以满足。<ref name="EWNov2014" />阿瑟顿饰演的派克在片中被斥“不是男人”，他还称，直到20世纪90年代中期还在街头遇到影迷以此相称，令他深感愤怒<ref name="FSR" /><ref name="HuffPoSep2014" />。

=== 家用媒体 ===
《捉鬼敢死队》的[[家用录像系统|VHS]]录像带1985年10月面世，[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]计划赶在本片前一天发布同样大卖的《比佛利山警探》录像带，哥伦比业影业为避免直接竞争提前一周发行。录像带定价79.95美元，本来市场前景良好，但显然无法同《比佛利山警探》低至29.95美元的定价竞争{{refn|group="注"|1985年的79.95和29.95美元分别相当于{{Inflation/year|US}}年{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|79.95|1985}}}}美元和{{Format price|{{Inflation|US|29.95|1985}}}}美元。}}。制片商为录像带发行投入一百万美元用于广告宣传，发行首周在录像带畅销榜排第十，哥伦比亚转让录像带生产和分销权约赚得两千万美元<ref>{{cite web | first = Dennis | last = Hunt | title = 'Ghostbusters' Races 'Cop' To Video Stores | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-09-27-ca-18449-story.html | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308163005/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-09-27-ca-18449-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1985-09-27 | access-date = 2021-11-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = The Man Re-Animating Disney | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1985/12/29/magazine/the-man-re-animating-disney.html | website =  The New York Times | date = 1985-12-29 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-06-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210602232518/https://www.nytimes.com/1985/12/29/magazine/the-man-re-animating-disney.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Dennis | last = Hunt | title = Mulling Over 'History Of White People' | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-11-01-ca-1058-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1985-11-01 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210309070919/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-11-01-ca-1058-story.html}}</ref>。《捉鬼敢死队》41万本VHS录像带的订购量创下新纪录，但几个月后就被42.5万本《[[第一滴血2|第一滴血2]]》超越。1986年2月，估计电影VHS录像带已售出40万本，收入3200万美元，在1985年电影VHS畅销榜排第三，仅次于《[[星际旅行III：石破天惊|星际旅行III：石破天惊]]》（42.5万本，1270万美元）和《比佛利山警探》（140万本，4190万美元）。<ref>{{cite news | last = Harmetz | first = Aljean | date = 1986-02-02 | title = Next video-cassette boom may be mass market sales | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1320&dat=19860202&id=77QRAAAAIBAJ&pg=2690,550249&hl=en | work = The Gainesville Sun | location = Gainesville, Florida | page = E1 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190629101159/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1320&dat=19860202&id=77QRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6OkDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2690,550249&hl=en<!-- Backup archive.is/4tAwc --> | archive-date = 2019-06-29 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

