6 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210906164359/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/ghostbusters-theme-gets-glowing-vinyl-reissue-for-record-store-day-236005/}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine | first = Daniel | last = Kreps | title = 'Ghostbusters' Theme Gets 30th Anniversary Marshmallow-Scented Reissue | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/ghostbusters-theme-gets-30th-anniversary-marshmallow-scented-reissue-41751/ | magazine = Rolling Stone | date = 2014-10-12 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url= http://web.archive.org/web/20210906153031/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/ghostbusters-theme-gets-30th-anniversary-marshmallow-scented-reissue-41751/ | archive-date = 2021-09-06 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。2019年6月，伯恩斯坦谱写的配乐经[[雷射唱片|雷射唱片]]、数字下载、[[黑膠唱片|黑膠唱片]]发布，发含四首未面世曲目和伯恩斯坦之子彼得的评论音轨<ref>{{cite web | title = Sony Pictures Launches Ghostbusters™ 35th Anniversary Celebration | url = https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sony-pictures-launches-ghostbusters-35th-anniversary-celebration-300863750.html | date = 2019-06-07 | website = [[美通社|PRNewswire.com]] | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308213138/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sony-pictures-launches-ghostbusters-35th-anniversary-celebration-300863750.html | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 商品 ===
{{see also|魔鬼剋星系列}}
《捉鬼敢死队》问世之际，电影商品尚属新鲜事物，制片商是在《星球大战》周边商品大卖后才逐渐跟进<ref name="NYTimesJun1989">{{cite web | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = Movie Merchandise: The Rush Is On | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1989/06/14/movies/movie-merchandise-the-rush-is-on.html | website =  The New York Times | date = 1989-06-14 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-05-17 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210517181032/https://www.nytimes.com/1989/06/14/movies/movie-merchandise-the-rush-is-on.html | page = C19}}</ref>。《捉鬼敢死队》表现远超预期，哥伦比亚影业没有制订全面的周边商品销售计划，无法充分利用电影人气巅峰时期的优势<ref name="ColliderNov2013">{{cite web | first = David | last = Kobylanski | title = You Know Who To Call Part 2: A Detailed Look at Recent ''Ghostbusters'' Toys, Video Games, Comics, and Merchandise | url = https://collider.com/ghostbusters-toys-video-games-comics/ | website = Collider | date = 2013-11-03 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211110024537/https://collider.com/ghostbusters-toys-video-games-comics/ | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。不过他们把颇具人气的“鬼魂免进”商标印上各种商品，产生额外收入<ref name="rs 2016">{{cite magazine | first = Charles | last = Bramsco | url =  https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/how-ghostbusters-gave-birth-to-the-modern-blockbuster-121570/ | title = How 'Ghostbusters' Gave Birth to the Modern Blockbuster | date = 2016-06-08 | access-date = 2021-11-16 | magazine = Rolling Stone | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211110030312/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-news/how-ghostbusters-gave-birth-to-the-modern-blockbuster-121570/}}</ref>。大部分热卖商品是1986年热门动画衍生剧《捉鬼特工队》问世后购买版权的其他企业所推<ref name="ColliderNov2013" />，直接源自本片的商品起初销售疲软，直到《捉鬼特工队》开播才改善，该剧1988年产生的商品销售收入达两亿美元，捉鬼敢死队质子背包是同年英国最流行的玩具<ref>{{cite web | first = Andrew | last = Hough | title = Transformers robots 'Britain's most popular toy' over past 25 years | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/retailandconsumer/8017063/Transformers-robots-Britains-most-popular-toy-over-past-25-years.html | website = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2010-09-22 | archive-url= http://web.archive.org/web/20210308202857/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/retailandconsumer/8017063/Transformers-robots-Britains-most-popular-toy-over-past-25-years.html}}</ref><ref name="NYTimesJun1989" />。电影上映同期发售的[[魔鬼克星_(游戏)|同名游戏]]颇为畅销<ref>{{cite web | title = The Making Of Ghostbusters | url = https://www.retrogamer.net/retro_games80/the-making-of-ghostbusters/ | dead-url = no | date = 2014-04-04 | website = Retro Gamer | access-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308140948/https://www.retrogamer.net/retro_games80/the-making-of-ghostbusters/}}</ref>，影片还有两部[[小说化|改编小说]]，其中拉里·米尔恩的同名作品与本片同期发布，理查德·穆勒的《捉鬼敢死队：超自然奇观》1985年问世<ref name="IndieWireJun2012" />。雷米斯1985年推出注释剧本《制作捉鬼敢死队》<ref name="VanityFair2014" />。

