https://edition.cnn.com/2011/09/25/living/ernest-cline-author-interview/index.html | archive-date = 2021-01-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>、电视<ref>{{cite web | first = James | last = Whitbrook | title = Stranger Things Had to Ask Permission to Use ''Ghostbusters'' Halloween Costumes | url = https://gizmodo.com/stranger-things-had-to-ask-permission-to-use-ghostbuste-1819838812 | website = io9 | date = 2017-10-25 | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210225203718/https://io9.gizmodo.com/stranger-things-had-to-ask-permission-to-use-ghostbuste-1819838812}}</ref>、电子游戏等各种传媒明确提及《捉鬼敢死队》或致敬<ref>{{cite web | first = Eddie | last = Makuch | title = Ghostbusters Content Coming to Family Guy Mobile Game | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ghostbusters-content-coming-to-family-guy-mobile-g/1100-6422716/ | website = GameSpot | date = 2015-03-18 | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308231025/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ghostbusters-content-coming-to-family-guy-mobile-g/1100-6422716/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Charlie | last = Hall | title = The Ghostbusters coming to Planet Coaster in bizarre DLC crossover | url = https://www.polygon.com/2019/5/22/18635693/planet-coaster-ghostbusters-dlc | date = 2019-05-22 | website = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20201108003406/https://www.polygon.com/2019/5/22/18635693/planet-coaster-ghostbusters-dlc | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。艾克洛德在1995年电影《[[鬼马小精灵_(电影)|鬼马小精灵]]》客串饰演雷·史坦茲<ref name="DigitalSpyMar18" />，片尾的庆祝游戏为2012年超级英雄片《[[復仇者聯盟|復仇者聯盟]]》结尾提供灵感，展现世界各地居民庆祝电影同名团体战胜外星侵略者<ref>{{cite web | first = Matt | last = Fowler | title = Kevin Feige Explains How Ghostbusters Influenced the End of The Avengers | date = 2019-11-16 | website = IGN | url = https://sea.ign.com/the-avengers-1998-1/155437/news/kevin-