=== 时代考验 ===
白驹过隙，《捉鬼敢死队》顶住时间考验，积极反响延续多年，在喜剧电影史上已有一席之地<ref name="ScreeNRantJul16" />。影片登上2013年参考书《死前必看的1001部电影》<ref>{{cite book| last = Schneider | first = Steven Jay | title = 1001 Movies You Must See Before You Die | date = 2013 | publisher = Murdoch Books Pty Limited | location = [[波士顿|Boston]], Massachusetts | isbn = 978-0-7641-6613-6 | page = 708}}</ref>。2014年《捉鬼敢死队》30周年之际，《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的娱乐业投票将本片排在影史佳片第77位<ref>{{cite web | title = Hollywood's 100 Favorite Films | url= https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/100-best-films-ever-hollywood-favorites-818512/ | date = 2014-06-25 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211112211924/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/100-best-films-ever-hollywood-favorites-818512/ | archive-date = 2021-11-12 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《[[Time_Out|Time Out]]》同年给予《捉鬼敢死队》五星（最高）好评并有“纯粹狂欢”美誉<ref>{{cite web | first = Tom | last = Huddleston | title = Ghostbusters | website= Time Out | date = 2014-10-27 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.timeout.com/london/film/ghostbusters | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210308142556/https://www.timeout.com/london/film/ghostbusters}}</ref>。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》读者投票评选百大佳片，本片排第68<ref>{{cite web | first = Willow | last = Green | title = The 100 Greatest Movies | date = 2021-03-24 | website = Empire | archive-date = 2021-11-16 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/best-movies-2/ | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211116223834/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/best-movies-2/}}</ref>。2014年《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滚石]]》读者经投票把《捉鬼敢死队》排在20世纪80年代佳片第九位<ref>{{cite web | title = Readers' Poll: The 25 Greatest Movies of the 1980s | date = 2014-02-19 | work = Rolling Stone | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210309062149/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-lists/readers-poll-the-25-greatest-movies-of-the-1980s-10686/23-st-elmos-fire-214856/ | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-lists/readers-poll-the-25-greatest-movies-of-the-1980s-10686/23-st-elmos-fire-214856/}}</ref>。评论汇总网站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]共收集本片73篇评论，认可度达九成七，平均评分8.1（最高十分）。网站共识写道：“特效与喜剧极具感染力的有趣组合，比尔面无表情的演出令人捧腹，引领大量了不起的喜剧转折。”<ref>{{cite web | website = [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]| title = Ghostbusters | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghostbusters | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211110230505/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghostbusters | dead-url = no}}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据八篇评论打出平均分71（最高100），代表“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghostbusters | title = Ghostbusters 1984 | website = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210521091914/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghostbusters | archive-date = 2021-05-21 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-17}}</ref>。

2001年，[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]评选[[AFI百年百大喜劇電影|百年百大喜剧片]]，《捉鬼敢死队》排第28<ref>{{cite web | title = AFI's 100 Years...100 Laughs | access-date = 2021-11-17 | url = https://www.afi.com/afis-100-years-100-laughs/ | website = [[美国电影学会|American Film Institute]] | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211114001438/https://www.afi.com/afis-100-years-100-laughs/ | archive-date = 2021-11-14 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《[[國家評論|國家評論]]》2009年评选过去25年25部最佳保守派电影，本片排第十，强调影片把“以规管为乐”的美国国家环境保护局描绘成反派，最后全靠私营部门挽回局面<ref>{{cite web | title = The Best Conservative Movies | date = 2009-02-23 | website = [[國家評論|National Review]] | url = https://www.nationalreview.com/magazine/2009/02/23/best-conservative-movies/ | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url= http://web.archive.org/web/20210911081527/https://www.nationalreview.com/magazine/2009/02/23/best-conservative-movies/ | archive-date = 2021-09-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。2015年11月，电影剧本在[[美国编剧工会|美国编剧工会]]评选的101部最有趣剧本排第14<ref>{{cite web | title = 101 Funniest Screenplays List | url = https://www.wga.org/writers-room/101-best-lists/101-funniest-screenplays/list | website = WGA.org | date = 2015-11-15 | access-date = 2021-11-18 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210718080410/https://www.wga.org/writers-room/101-best-lists/101-funniest-screenplays/list | archive-date = 2021-07-18 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]2017年邀请52个国家和地区的253名评论家（118男、135女）评选史上最搞笑电影，《捉鬼敢死队》位居第95<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20170821-the-100-greatest-comedies-of-all-time | title = The 100 Greatest Comedies of all Time | date = 2017-08-22 | website = [[英国广播公司|BBC]] | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211112004752/https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20170821-the-100-greatest-comedies-of-all-time | archive-date = 2021-11-12 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

