t films of all time | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/0/best-comedy-movies-funniest-films-time/ghostbusters-1984/ | website = The Daily Telegraph | date = 2017-03-24 | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210309064036/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/0/best-comedy-movies-funniest-films-time/ghostbusters-1984/}}</ref>、烂番茄网站第45<ref>{{cite web | title = 150 Essential Comedy Movies to Watch Now | url = https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/essential-comedy-movies/ | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211027110410/https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/essential-comedy-movies/ | archive-date = 2021-10-27 | access-date = 2021-11-17 | website = Rotten Tomatoes | dead-url = no}}</ref>，烂番茄评比三百部必看电影（未排名），本片再度上榜<ref>{{cite web | title = 200 Essential Movies to Watch Now | website =  Rotten Tomatoes | url = https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/essential-movies-to-watch-now/ | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-11-08 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211108004416/https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/essential-movies-to-watch-now/}}</ref>。此外，电影还在最佳科幻片<ref>{{cite web | first1 = Alex | last1 = Plim | first2 = Tom | last2 = Huddleston | first3 = Geoff | last3 = Andrew | first4 = Catherine | last4 = Bray | first5 = Dave | last5 = Calhoun | first6 = Cath | last6 = Clarke | first7 = Alex | last7 = Dudok de Wit | first8 = Eddy | last8 = Frankel | first9 = Trevor | last9 = Johnston | display-authors = etal | title = The 100 best sci-fi movies | access-date = 2021-11-17 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.timeout.com/london/film/the-100-best-sci-fi-movies | date = 2018-12-12 | website = Time Out | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211106213625/https://www.timeout.com/london/film/the-100-best-sci-fi-movies | archive-date = 2021-11-06}}</ref>、最佳科幻喜剧<ref>{{cite web | first1 = Alasdair | last1 = Wilkins | first2 = Charlie Jane | last2 = Anders | title = The 13 Greatest Science Fiction Comedies Of All Time | dead-url = no | url = https://gizmodo.com/the-13-greatest-science-fiction-comedies-of-all-time-1613425431 | website = io9 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210719103810/https://gizmodo.com/the-13-greatest-science-fiction-comedies-of-all-time-1613425431 | date = 2014-07-30 | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-07-19}}</ref>、最佳暑期大片评选榜上有名<ref name="EWApr14" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Matt | last = Fowler | title = The 25 Best Summer Blockbusters of All Time | date = 2019-07-01 | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-10-27 | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/07/01/the-25-best-summer-blockbusters-of-all-time | website = IGN | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211027011549/https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/07/01/the-25-best-summer-blockbusters-of-all-time | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《帝国杂志》2006年评选“伟大电影角色百强”，默瑞饰演的彼得·威克曼位居第44<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.empireonline.com/100-greatest-movie-characters/default.asp?c=44 | title = The 100 Greatest Movie Characters- 44. Peter Venkman | website = Empire | access-date = 2011-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111107044800/http://www.empireonline.com/100-greatest-movie-characters/default.asp?c=44 | archive-date = 2011-11-07 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>，2020年再度评选升至第31<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/100-greatest-movie-characters/ | title = The 100 Greatest Movie Characters | website = Empire | access-date = 2021-11-17 | date = 2020-10-08 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211111201701/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/100-greatest-movie-characters/ | archive-date = 2021-11-11 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 续作与改编 ==
