[[File:Harold_Ramis_memorial.jpg|thumb]]去世，第二部续集的拍摄计划由重启取代。影迷在梯形消防站公司8号旁留下纪念品悼念雷米斯<ref name="ScreeNRantJul16" />]]

电影叫好叫座，催生包括动画电视剧、续集与重启电影在内的[[魔鬼剋星系列|魔鬼剋星系列]]<ref name="CBRJan18">{{cite web | first = Kelvin | last = Childs | title = Something Strange: 15 Dark Secrets About The Real Ghostbusters | url = https://www.cbr.com/dark-secrets-real-ghostbusters/ | website = Comic Book Resources | date = 2018-01-05 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210817085741/https://www.cbr.com/dark-secrets-real-ghostbusters/ | access-date = 2021-11-17 | archive-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。1986年的动画电视剧《捉鬼特工队》持续播映六年，播出七季共140集，该剧又催生漫画、商品，还有以斯林姆为核心的节目，并在1997年推出电视剧续作《[[极端捉鬼特工队|极端捉鬼特工队]]》<ref name="CBRJan18" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Stephen | last = Harber | title = Extreme Ghostbusters Is a Lot Better Than You Remember | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/tv/extreme-ghostbusters-is-a-lot-better-than-you-remember/ | website = Den of Geek | date = 2016-07-18 | access-date = 2021-11-18 | archive-date = 2021-10-11 | dead-url = no | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20211011043125/https://www.denofgeek.com/tv/extreme-ghostbusters-is-a-lot-better-than-you-remember/}}</ref>。1989年的续集电影《[[魔鬼剋星2|魔鬼剋星2]]》打破多项票房纪录，估计首周末观影人数超原作两百万，但无论票房总成绩还是评论都有不及<ref>{{cite news | first = Claudia | last = Puig | title = Record-Busting Opening for 'Ghostbusters II | newspaper = Los Angeles Times | date = 1989-06-20 | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-06-20-ca-2613-story.html | access-date = 2020-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190719210442/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-06-20-ca-2613-story.html | archive-date = 2019-07-19 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="VultureAug14">{{cite journal | first = Brian | last = Feldman | title = A Roundup of Every Ghostbusters 3 Rumor From the Past 25 Years | url = https://www.vulture.com/2014/08/ghostbusters-3-rumors-timeline.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035536/http://www.vulture.com/2014/08/ghostbusters-3-rumors-timeline.html | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no | journal = Vulture | date = 2014-08-07 | access-date = 2020-12-02}}</ref>。演员和角色的人气还在，《捉鬼敢死队》仍有望推出第二部续作<ref name="VultureAug14" />，但因默瑞无意参与持续多年缺乏进展。他在2009年接受采访时表示：<blockquote>我们拍了（《捉鬼敢死队2》），但我不大满意，在我看来只有第一部才有实际价值，续集没啥意思……成片（与原有构想）完全不同……至少我对第二部非常失望，根本没考虑《捉鬼敢死队3》<ref>{{cite web | first = Adam | last = Sweeney | title = Bill Murray Ain't Afraid of No Ghostbusters Sequel | archive-date = 2019-07-17 | dead-url = yes | url = https://filmschoolrejects.com/bill-murray-aint-afraid-of-no-ghostbusters-sequel/ | website = Film School Rejects | date = 2008-10-07 | access-date = 2019-07-17 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20190717221626/https://filmschoolrejects.com/bill-murray-aint-afraid-of-no-ghostbusters-sequel/}}</ref>。</blockquote>艾克洛德直到21世纪10年代初都没有放弃下一部续集的开发计划<ref name="VultureAug14" />，他和雷米斯为2009年的《[[捉鬼敢死队：电子游戏|捉鬼敢死队：电子游戏]]》情节创作担任顾问，两人和莫瑞、哈德森、波茨、阿瑟頓均为游戏配音。故事情节发生在《捉鬼敢死队2》过去两年后，玩家是捉鬼大队新成员，对付与戈泽有关的鬼魂威胁。游戏广受好评，情节表述获奖项提名，艾克洛德声称该作“本质上就是第三部电影”。<ref name="VultureAug14" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Philip | last = Tibbets | title = Why the Ghostbusters game is "essentially the third movie" | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/games/why-the-ghostbusters-game-is-essentially-the-third-movie/ | website = Den of Geek | date = 2014-06-02 | access-date = 2020-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112405/https://www.denofgeek.com/games/why-the-ghostbusters-game-is-essentially-the-third-movie/ | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | dead-url = no}}</ref>原作首部续作小说《捉鬼敢死队归来》原计划2004年发售，但尚未落实出版社便告破产。另外还有许多[[捉鬼敢死队_(漫画)|漫画作品]]延继电影人物旅程，走遍世界各地甚至到达其他空间。<ref name="ScreeNRantJul16" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Graeme | last = McMillan | title = Remembering the Long Forgotten 'Ghostbusters' Spinoffs Through the Years | url= https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/ghostbusters-spinoffs-a-brief-history-888253/ | date = 2016-04-27 | website = The Hollywood Reporter | access-date = 2021-11-18 | archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20210817085738/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/ghostbusters-spinoffs-a-brief-history-888253/ | archive-date = 2021-08-17 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

2014年雷米斯去世后，雷特曼认为与雷米斯、艾克洛德、默瑞共同掌控版权对系列作品发展不利，开始与哥伦比亚影业谈判转让版权，还花两周说服默瑞。他没有透露交易细节，只表示“创作者能让我们和后人的生活过得充实”。雷特曼与艾克洛德创办[[鬼魂制片公司|鬼魂制片公司]]延续和扩张《捉鬼敢死队》系列，首先推出的是2016年重启之作《[[魔鬼剋星_(2016年電影)|-{zh-cn:超能敢死队;zh-tw:魔鬼剋星;zh-hk:捉鬼敢死隊;zh-sg:捉鬼敢死队;}-]]》，[[保罗·费格|保罗·费格]]执导<ref>{{cite journal | last = Zuckerman | first = Esther | date = 2014-10-08 | title = Paul Feig explains his vision for a female-led 'Ghostbusters' | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112042430/https://ew.com/article/2014/10/08/paul-feig-ghostbusters-female/ | journal = Entertainment Weekly | url = https://ew.com/article/2014/10/08/paul-feig-ghostbusters-female/ | access-date = 2020-12-02 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Siegel | first1 = Tatiana | last2 = Kit | first2 = Borys | title = 'Ghostbusters III' Script to Be Reworked Following Harold Ramis' Death | date = 2014-02-25 | journal = The Hollywood Reporter | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-iii-script-be-reworked-683518 | access-date = 2020-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201119184213/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ghostbusters-iii-script-be-reworked-683518 | archive-date = 2020-11-19 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | first = Jada | last = Yuan | title = Ivan Reitman on Bill Murray, Internet Trolls, and Why He Fought for the Ghostbusters Reboot | url = https://www.vulture.com/2016/07/ivan-reitman-ghostbusters-bill-murray-qa.html | journal = Vulture | date = 2016-07-14 | access-date = 2020-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127073651/https://www.vulture.com/2016/07/ivan-reitman-ghostbusters-bill-murray-qa.html | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-31016868 | title = Ghostbusters female line-up confirmed | website = BBC News Online | date = 2015-01-28 | access-date = 2020-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130151945/https://